NK015(ba)025:0: sngon 'gro me tog phreng mdzes kyi 'grel pa'i dabu'o //
NK015(ba)025:2: bla ma yi dam bka' sdod rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:3: chos sku nam mkha' yangs pa'i dkyil //
NK015(ba)025:4: longs sku nyi ma'i gdul bya la //
NK015(ba)025:5: sprul sku tsha zer dpag med 'phros //
NK015(ba)025:6: kun mkhyen pad mo'i gnyen la 'dud //
NK015(ba)025:7: des bstan rgyud rgyal gsang snying gi //
NK015(ba)025:8: rgyud don bsgrub thabs ltar bshad pa'i //
NK015(ba)025:9: cho ga sbyor dngos rjes gsum la //
NK015(ba)025:10: sngon 'gro'i gsal byed bri bar bya /
NK015(ba)025:12: / 'dir rgyud sde thams cad kyi rgyal po chen po
NK015(ba)025:13: dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i don bsgrub thabs dang 'brel
NK015(ba)025:14: zhing / bsgrub thabs man ngag dang 'brel la /
NK015(ba)025:15: man ngag bla ma dam pa'i phyag len dang 'brel yang /
NK015(ba)025:16: phyag len cho ga'i 'grig dang 'brel ba'i lugs ltar bshad na /
NK015(ba)025:17: le'u bcu bzhi yan chad ni ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor zhi ba yin la /
NK015(ba)025:18: bco lnga man chad bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor yin /
NK015(ba)025:20: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim bsdebs ma shes na /
NK015(ba)025:21: bdud rtsi ro snyoms lta bu'i bshad par 'gro ba'i skyon yod pas /
NK015(ba)025:23: cho ga sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyis bstan dgos ste /
NK015(ba)025:25: sbyor dngos rjes gsum mi mkhas pas //
NK015(ba)025:26: skyes bu rnams ni ci ltar yang //
NK015(ba)025:27: ci bsgrub bya ba nges med yin //
NK015(ba)025:28: mthar phyin bya ba shin tu dka' /
NK015(ba)025:30: / ces gsung pas 'di ni sbyor ba sngon 'gro'i chos so //
NK015(ba)025:35: gnas khang gis brtag pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:36: dkyil 'khor rtsigs shing chag chag gdab pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:38: nang du 'dug nas tshul phyag dang gral phyag bya ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:39: gong ma rnams ni bsgrub gzhung rnams su shes la /
NK015(ba)025:40: gsum pa p+au tsa bsham pa la /
NK015(ba)025:43: mchod pa'i rdzas bsham pa dang gsum mo //
NK015(ba)025:46: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK015(ba)025:50: ri mo rgyu bzhis 'bur blug dang /
NK015(ba)025:57: de yang zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis gtso
NK015(ba)025:58: bo byas pa'i zhi ba'i lha tshogs g.yas su bsham
NK015(ba)025:59: / lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyis gtso bo byas pa'i khro bo'i lha tshogs g.yon du bsham /
NK015(ba)025:60: bla ma'i sku gzugs la sogs pa rnams dbus su bsham /
NK015(ba)025:61: de rnams kun g.yas kyi nang tshan no //
NK015(ba)025:62: gnyis pa gsung rten glegs bam gang yod g.yon du bsham /
NK015(ba)025:63: gsum pa thugs rten gdung ring bsrel la sogs pa rnams dbus su bsham /
NK015(ba)025:67: gnyis med kyi rgyud thams cad dbus su bsham /
NK015(ba)025:68: 'ga' zhig gi zhi khro thabs shes kyi sgo nas g.yas g.yon du bsham pa yin zer ste /
NK015(ba)025:70: gdul bya lugs 'byung ldog gi dbang gis /
NK015(ba)025:71: ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)025:72: bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:74: rgyud nas kyang de ltar du bshad de /
NK015(ba)025:75: de dag gis dgos ched ni rnal 'byor pa la byin rlabs 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK015(ba)025:76: gnyis pa mchod pa'i rgyan la gsum las /
NK015(ba)025:80: gdugs 'phan la sogs pa rnams steng du phub /
NK015(ba)025:84: 'dod yon gyi lha mo la sogs pa logs su bsham /
NK015(ba)025:86: phyag bdar legs por byas la /
NK015(ba)025:87: de'i steng du dpyang la sogs pa bting ba'i steng du many+dzi la sogs pa bsham /
NK015(ba)025:88: gzhan yang phyag mtshan rdo rje dril bu /
NK015(ba)025:89: rnge'u chung la sogs pa rol mo'i bye brag kyang bsham ste /
NK015(ba)025:90: bsham lugs mchod sprin chen po'i mdo las bshad /
NK015(ba)025:92: lha mnyes shing rnal 'byor pa tshogs rdzogs pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK015(ba)025:93: gsum pa mchod rdzas bsham pa la /
NK015(ba)025:94: rtsa ba'am nang gis mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:95: yan lag phyi'i mchod pa bsham lugs dang gnyis te /
NK015(ba)025:96: de yang mchod sprin chen po'i mdo las //
NK015(ba)025:97: dbang dang ldan pa'i stegs bu ru //
NK015(ba)025:98: lnga dang gsum gnyis p+au tsa bsham //
NK015(ba)025:99: gtor mgo g.yas la mchod mgo g.yon //
NK015(ba)025:100: ring ba rgyab la thung ba mdun /
NK015(ba)025:102: / 'gul snol rtse sprad yang dog sbyar //
NK015(ba)025:103: many+dzi ngos bzung rang la bstan //
NK015(ba)025:104: ces gsung pas many+dzi la ring ba rnams rgyab nas phar la bsham /
NK015(ba)025:105: thung ba rnams mdun na tshur bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:106: de la dang po rtsa ba'i nang mchod sman rag gtor gsum bsham lugs ni /
NK015(ba)025:107: sman b+han+d+ha mtshan nyid ldan pa'i nang du /
NK015(ba)025:108: chang phud ma nyams pa gtsong ma la pany+tsa btab la rang gis g.yas su bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:110: b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan lcang lo can gyi nang du /
NK015(ba)025:111: phyi'i rak+ta dpa' bo grir shi ba'i khrag /
NK015(ba)025:114: gsang ba'i rak+ta ni bu mo gtsang ma rdo rje'i
NK015(ba)025:115: mda' ma phog pa'i rak+ta rnams la gzhi blang ba'i
NK015(ba)025:117: a mri ta btab la rang gi g.yon du bsham /
NK015(ba)025:118: gtor ma ni chos bcu las /
NK015(ba)025:119: mchog gi dngos grub grub bya'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:120: dang po zas kyi phud la bya //
NK015(ba)025:122: dang po gtor ma'i rgyu ni /
NK015(ba)025:126: dpyid yin na zan la gtor ma bya zhes kyang gsung /
NK015(ba)025:130: zhi ba rnams chang gi sbrus la /
NK015(ba)025:131: pad gtor pad sdong gi tshul la theb skyu pad 'dab kyi tshul du bya /
NK015(ba)025:132: khro bo dang chos skyongs drag byed rnams la /
NK015(ba)025:133: phye gtsang ma la sha sna snying sna rnams kyi phye ma bsres la chang dang rak+tasa sbrus zhing /
NK015(ba)025:134: dpal gtor snying gi tshul du bya /
NK015(ba)025:135: theb skyu rnams don snying 'byin pa'i tshul lam /
NK015(ba)025:136: thod tshal gyi tshul byas la /
NK015(ba)025:137: mar zhal dang sha chen la sogs pas brgyan cing a mri ta btab bo //
NK015(ba)025:139: 'khor gyi nyes skyon dag bya'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:140: snod de shin tu gtsang bar bya //
NK015(ba)025:142: gtor snod ka p+aa la dum bu gcig pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:143: snod gtsang ma'i nang du bsham zhing bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)025:144: snod de shin tu bkang bar bya //
NK015(ba)025:146: snod de yang shin tu bkang la //
NK015(ba)025:147: gtor len blang dor med pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:148: gtor tshug gcig tu brtag par bya //
NK015(ba)025:150: gtor ma ma skyong ba la dus drug gam bzhi
NK015(ba)025:151: la sogs pa la snga phyi med par dus cing
NK015(ba)025:152: mi g.yo ba'o // yang na rgyu la bzang ngan med pa la zer /
NK015(ba)025:153: kha cig gis dus rgyun du gtor tshug che chung med pa gcig tu brtag par bya /
NK015(ba)025:155: bsnyen bkur dag dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:156: many+dzi la sogs stegs la bzhag /
NK015(ba)025:158: gtor ma de smin mtshams pas mi mtho //
NK015(ba)025:159: thugs ka bas mi dma' ba'i stegs la bzhag pa la /
NK015(ba)025:160: gtor ma dbus su bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:162: 'ga' zhig gis g.yas g.yon thabs shes kyi cha yin zer yang /
NK015(ba)025:164: ma h+aa b+ha ling a mri ta /
NK015(ba)025:165: dmar chen tshogs kyi gtor ma dgram /
NK015(ba)025:167: / 'di la smar ston seng ge 'od kyis dpal chen po'i g.yas zhal dkar po la sman /
NK015(ba)025:168: g.yon zhal dmar po la rak+ta /
NK015(ba)025:169: dbus zhal mthing ka la gtor ma bstabs pa'i brda
NK015(ba)025:170: yin pas g.yas g.yon dbus gsum de ltar du yin
NK015(ba)025:171: gsungs so // gnyis pa yan lag gam phyi'i p+au tsa bsham pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:174: zangs la sogs pa snod gtsang ma'i nang du /
NK015(ba)025:176: chu bo chen po'i chu la /
NK015(ba)025:177: ba dmar ser gyi 'o ma blug /
NK015(ba)025:181: spos sbyor dang ldan pa'i spos rgya'am /
NK015(ba)025:183: khro bo la sha chen gyi bdug spos bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:185: dbyar yin na chu dang thang la skyes pa'i me tog /
NK015(ba)025:186: dgun yin na 'bru la sman gyis kha dog bsgyur ba'o /
NK015(ba)025:188: / 'bru sil ma'i me tog bsham mo /
NK015(ba)025:189: khro bo la dbang po lnga'i me tog bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:190: de'i 'og tu zhum mar gyi mar me mtshan nyid dang ldan pa bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:191: khro bo la tshil chen gyi mar me bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:193: dung chos sam snod gtsang ma'i nang du chu gtsang blug la /
NK015(ba)025:195: a ka ru dang du ru ka la sogs pa'i dri bzang po rnams btab la bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:196: khro bo la dri chu'i dri chab bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:198: zhi ba la 'bras bu'i zhal zas /
NK015(ba)025:199: khro bo la dri chen gyi zhal zas bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:201: zhi ba la rol mo'i bye brag /
NK015(ba)025:202: khro bo la rkang gling thod rnga la sogs pa rnams bsham /
NK015(ba)025:203: de ltar mchod pa de dag bsham lugs la /
NK015(ba)025:204: sman rag gtor gsum bsham lugs lam rim las bshad /
NK015(ba)025:205: rnam lnga bsham lugs mchod sprin chen po las bshad /
NK015(ba)025:206: de ni gral thabs su bsham pa'i dbang du'o //
NK015(ba)025:208: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rang dbang che ba'i rang
NK015(ba)025:209: dbang du mchod mgo g.yon bstan nas g.yas su bskor
NK015(ba)025:215: nub tu zhal zas rnams bsham /
NK015(ba)025:216: gtor mgo g.yas su bstan nas g.yon skor du bsham la /
NK015(ba)025:222: nub tu dam can rnams bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:223: sman raka dang bsang chu snod gtsang ma'i nang du
NK015(ba)025:224: chu gtsang la ga bur la sogs pa'i dri bzang
NK015(ba)025:225: btab la rang gis mdun nas g.yas gral byed pa'i
NK015(ba)025:226: bsang chu sman raka rim par bsham mo //
NK015(ba)025:227: bzhi pa skabs 'dir rgyud gzhung dang stod zur pa tshang gi lugs la tshul phyag dang /
NK015(ba)025:233: phyi nang gi mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:235: rnal 'byor pa rnams nang du 'dus la /
NK015(ba)025:237: lag sor dpa' bo'i 'bru lnga gsal bas /
NK015(ba)025:238: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dza /
NK015(ba)025:239: zhes rdo rje go 'byed kyi mu tra dang bcas pa lan gsum brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:240: lan dang pos se gol g.yas su gtogs pas zhi
NK015(ba)025:241: ba'i lha tshogs spyan drangs nas g.yas kyi nam mkha'
NK015(ba)025:242: la bzhugs / lan gnyis pas se gol g.yon du
NK015(ba)025:243: gtogs pas khro bo'i lha tshogs spyan drangs nas g.yon
NK015(ba)025:245: lan gsum pa se gol dbus su gtogs pas bla
NK015(ba)025:246: ma rig 'dzin byang sems mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams
NK015(ba)025:247: spyan drangs nas dbus su bzhugs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:248: rab rgyun bshags byas la phyag 'tshal lam /
NK015(ba)025:250: de ma grub na phyag rkyang pa 'tshal de /
NK015(ba)025:253: rig 'dzin byang sems mkha' 'gro chos skyong la gsum /
NK015(ba)025:254: yang na bla ma rig 'dzin byang sems mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams la gsum /
NK015(ba)025:256: bsgrub khang rnying pa yin na gnas bdag la gsum 'tshal /
NK015(ba)025:258: de nas ru gdan la bzhugs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:260: de nas dbang rdzogs par thob gang snga ba rnams gral rim du bsdad pa /
NK015(ba)025:261: 'og ma 'og ma rnams kyi phyag gsum gsum 'tshal lo /
NK015(ba)025:263: / 'o na tshul phyag dang gral phyag gi don ni /
NK015(ba)025:264: lam rim gyis 'jug tshul dang bstun na /
NK015(ba)025:265: thog mar skyabs 'gro dang phyag 'tshal dgos pas /
NK015(ba)025:266: de dang tshul mthun du byed pas tshul phyag /
NK015(ba)025:267: dbang thob pa'i rim pa ltar du gral du 'khod cing /
NK015(ba)025:268: gral rim ltar du 'tshal ba'i phyir gral phyag /
NK015(ba)025:270: rdo rje 'dus pas dbang gral du //
NK015(ba)025:271: nges pa'i don gyi gdung chen shar //
NK015(ba)025:274: / 'dir slob dpon dam pa bde bar gshegs pa'i lugs kyis /
NK015(ba)025:275: rab rgyun bshags ltar nyams su blang tshul la /
NK015(ba)025:276: rgyun bshags yan lag brgyad pa /
NK015(ba)025:279: dang po rgyun bshags rang la'ang sngon du bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:283: 'khor gyis gnod pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:284: gtor ma bzhag par mi bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:286: gtor ma bsham ma thag tu ma bsngo na yi dwags mkha' rgyu'i dri za rnams kyis brlabs cing /
NK015(ba)025:288: de ma bsngo na ye shes kyi lha la thugs rtog mi mnga' yang /
NK015(ba)025:289: de'i 'khor du gnas pa'i dregs byed rnams kyi gnod pa 'ong bas /
NK015(ba)025:290: bsham ma thag tu bsngo dgos ste /
NK015(ba)025:291: ma khom na'ang gtor chu blug pa kh+aa hi btag pa la //
NK015(ba)025:292: rten 'brel tshogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:293: bsang chab dag dang ldan par bya //
NK015(ba)025:295: dang po las slob pas gtor ma la chu gtsang gis bran la /
NK015(ba)025:296: thams cad kyis chab sbyang mdzad par zhu zhus pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:297: thams cad kyis swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+he sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa ba shud+d+ho &aham /
NK015(ba)025:299: rtsa sde ba'i phyag len la /
NK015(ba)025:300: gtor ma'i thugs dam chus mi bslad //
NK015(ba)025:302: chang gnyis bar du chu gcig blug par bzhed do //
NK015(ba)025:303: bar chad zhi bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:304: sngags kyis yang dag bsrung bar bya //
NK015(ba)025:306: las slob pas gtor ma la chang rgod bran la /
NK015(ba)025:307: gtor ma la skyems thal byin rlabs mdzad par zhu zhus pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:310: byin rlabs rtsa ba bka' brgyud bla ma mchod /
NK015(ba)025:311: dngos grub rtsa ba yi dam lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:312: phrin las rtsa ba chos skyongs srung ma /
NK015(ba)025:313: bsnyen bsgrub rtsa ba ma dang mkha' 'gro /
NK015(ba)025:314: bstan srung bka' sdod las mkhan pho nya dang bcas pa rnams mchod /
NK015(ba)025:315: ma h+aa b+ha ling+ta rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK015(ba)025:317: dngos su 'bul ba ma yin yang /
NK015(ba)025:318: bar chad bsrung ba'i don ste /
NK015(ba)025:319: dper na rgyal po la nor bsngo tshar na 'bang gzhan gyis lan mi spob pa dang 'dra bar /
NK015(ba)025:320: dkon mchog la 'bul rgyu yin byas pas mi ma yin gzhan gyis brlab tu med do //
NK015(ba)025:321: gzhan mchod pa 'bul ba'i yul ngos ma bzung sngon
NK015(ba)025:322: du mchod byas na gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha
NK015(ba)025:324: rgyun bshags dngos la dpang po bskyed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:325: bshags tshul yan lag brgyad pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:327: rnal 'byor pas dus rgyun du bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:331: lha dpang dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK015(ba)025:333: sngon 'gro'i thog mar yi dam gyi lha bsgom na
NK015(ba)025:334: yi dam gyi lha mi spang zhing dge ba gang
NK015(ba)025:336: de nas las slob pas spos sbyang byas te /
NK015(ba)025:338: de nas rnal 'byor pa tshogs pa rnams kyi mdun du 'dris zhing mthar rten drung du bzhag la /
NK015(ba)025:341: rang nyid pad zla'i steng du rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK015(ba)025:342: g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:343: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK015(ba)025:344: zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)025:345: sku snang la rang bzhin med pa bsgom pa'i khong la /
NK015(ba)025:346: khong stong lta bur gnas pa'i nang du rtsa ro dbu rkyang gsum yod pa /
NK015(ba)025:349: dbu ma yang zer ba'i rtsa /
NK015(ba)025:350: sbom phra mda' snyug tsam dkar la drang pa /
NK015(ba)025:351: gsal la stong pa'i rtsa mtshan nyid bzhi dang ldan pa gcig lte 'og sor bzhi nas /
NK015(ba)025:352: spyi bo'i tshang bug gi bar du ka ba btsug
NK015(ba)025:353: pa ltar du bsgom pa'i rtsa de'i nang thugs ka'i
NK015(ba)025:354: thad tsam du nyi ma zhabs zla ba steng du
NK015(ba)025:355: gnas pa'i ga'u kha sbyor du gnas pa'i nang du
NK015(ba)025:356: / sems kyi rang bzhin h'u dkar po gcig bsam mo //
NK015(ba)025:357: badz+ra sa ma na dza h'u dza /
NK015(ba)025:358: zhes brjod pas thugs ka'i h'u de las 'od zer kha dog sna lnga byung /
NK015(ba)025:359: srog dag pa'i lam du zhugs nas /
NK015(ba)025:360: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas thon te /
NK015(ba)025:361: 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhing khams thams cad la phog /
NK015(ba)025:362: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi sku zhi khro'i rnam pa bzhengs nas /
NK015(ba)025:363: mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs zhing nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:364: de yang zhi ba bsgom na zhi ba dbus dam rgyan g.yas /
NK015(ba)025:373: dam rgyan g.yon du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)025:374: gtso bo gang bsgom gyi dbu la zla dkyil gyi
NK015(ba)025:375: steng du sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun kun 'dus kyi
NK015(ba)025:376: ngo bo rdo rje slob dpon de dang /
NK015(ba)025:377: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams rdo rje sems dpa'i tshul du bzhugs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:378: ja 'dren gyi tshul du mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:379: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha a h+aum /
NK015(ba)025:387: gnyis pa bshags tshul la brgyad de /
NK015(ba)025:393: mya ngan las mi 'da' ba bzhugs su gsol ba /
NK015(ba)025:395: dam bca' smon lam gyi yan lag dang brgyad do //
NK015(ba)025:397: mchod rten nyi ma'i gzugs chen bzhugs /
NK015(ba)025:398: yan lag brgyad pa'i tshul bzung ba //
NK015(ba)025:400: rnam mkhyen thob pa'i thabs la /
NK015(ba)025:401: tshogs bsags cing sgrib pa sbyang dgos pa /
NK015(ba)025:402: mdo sngags thams cad mthun no //
NK015(ba)025:403: de'i rtsa ba yan lag bdun pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:406: spyir 'khor 'das bde sdug thams cad bdun rnam par dag pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:409: gsum gyis lag rjes yin te /
NK015(ba)025:410: bdun rnam par ma dag pas /
NK015(ba)025:411: phyag dang mchod pa'i 'os su mi 'gyur zhing /
NK015(ba)025:412: brnyas pa dang khyad gsod kyi gnas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:413: longs spyod kyis mthun rkyen gyis 'bong ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:414: mi dge ba la sogs pa'i lam du 'jug cing /
NK015(ba)025:415: gnas de dang de la sus kyang bzlog pa med pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:416: bya ba gang la yang thams cad yid mi rang zhing /
NK015(ba)025:417: thams cad skyo ba'i gnas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:418: theg pa chen po'i chos dang mi 'phrad zhing log pa'i lam du 'jug pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:419: yang dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang myur du bral zhing /
NK015(ba)025:420: rang nyid tshe thung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:421: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams chud zos zhing zad par 'gyur ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:422: bdun rnam par ma dag pas ni skyon de rnams byed la /
NK015(ba)025:423: cung zad dag pa'i yon tan gyis rang nyid phyag dang mchod pa'i gnas su 'gyur zhing /
NK015(ba)025:424: brnyas pa dang khyad gsod kyi gnas su mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:425: phun sum tshogs pa'i longs spyod kyis rgyas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:426: mi dge ba'i chos kyis mi gos zhing /
NK015(ba)025:427: dge ba rgyun mi chad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:428: bya ba thams cad la yi rang zhing bsod nams kyi phung po yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:429: theg pa chen po'i chos dang mjal zhing /
NK015(ba)025:430: chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi chad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:431: 'phags pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang mi 'bral zhing tshe la dbang thob pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:432: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa dam pa gnyis su smin pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:433: sa dang lam gyi yon tan thams cad bskyed la /
NK015(ba)025:434: bdun rnam par dag pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:435: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po /
NK015(ba)025:436: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi go 'phang thob pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:439: ma dag pa dang dag pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:440: shin tu rnam dag go rim bzhin //
NK015(ba)025:443: yan lag bdun pa kho na bsod nams bsags pa'i mchog tu gsungs shing /
NK015(ba)025:444: bsgrub thabs chung ngu re re'i mgo na yang /
NK015(ba)025:445: bdun rnam dag gi bsod nams bsags par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:447: 'di nyid mchog tu gyur pa yin no //
NK015(ba)025:448: thabs kyis dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad bsags sbyang gnyis su 'dus pa yin /
NK015(ba)025:449: myur du sangs rgyas pa la 'gal rkyen spang zhing /
NK015(ba)025:450: mthun rkyen tshang ba gcig dgos te /
NK015(ba)025:451: 'di la tshang ba sangs rgyas pa la /
NK015(ba)025:452: tshogs chen po yongs su rdzogs dgos pa la /
NK015(ba)025:453: phyag dang mchod pa'i yan lag /
NK015(ba)025:456: dge ba'i rtsa ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i dpung bskyed pa la /
NK015(ba)025:458: theg pa chen po'i chos dang mi 'bral bar dgos pa la /
NK015(ba)025:459: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:460: yang dag pa'i bshes gnyen dang mi 'bral bar dgos pa la /
NK015(ba)025:461: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:462: dge ba'i rtsa ba chud mi za zhing snying po len pas bsngo ba bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:463: brgyad pa dam bca' ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK015(ba)025:464: sngar blang ba'i dam tshig nyams na /
NK015(ba)025:465: 'di nyid kyis sor chud pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK015(ba)025:466: des na 'gal rkyen spang zhing mthun rkyen bsgrub dgos /
NK015(ba)025:467: de'i lam thams cad tshang ba yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:468: 'di nyid mchog tu gyur pa yin gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:469: de ltar yan lag brgyad kyi dang po phyag 'tshal ba la /
NK015(ba)025:470: bla ma dang dkon mchog gsum /
NK015(ba)025:471: yi dam la phyag 'tshal ba dang gsum las /
NK015(ba)025:472: dang po bla ma la phyag 'tshal ba la yang spyir phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:473: bla ma'i yon tan dran par byed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:474: phyag 'tshal ba dngos dang gsum las /
NK015(ba)025:476: rang gi lus sprul sku'i zhing gi rdul snyed du
NK015(ba)025:477: sprul nas lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal
NK015(ba)025:478: bar bsam la / 'das ma 'ongs da lta dusa
NK015(ba)025:479: gsum gyi sangsa rgyas thamsa cad kyi sku gsunga thugas
NK015(ba)025:480: kyi ngo bo nyid dang dbyer med cing /
NK015(ba)025:481: yida bzhina gyi nor bu rin po che dgos 'dod phun sum tshogs pa lta bu /
NK015(ba)025:482: yon tan phun sum tshogs pa'i bla mas dbang bskur
NK015(ba)025:483: rgyud bshad man ngag gnang ba'i chos 'brel yod tshad
NK015(ba)025:485: bla ma'i yon tan dran par byed pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:487: thams cad kyi blar gyur par na bla yon tan bskyed pas na ma /
NK015(ba)025:488: bshes gnyen dang mkhan po'i ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK015(ba)025:489: spyir gsang sngags pas gtso cher bla ma /
NK015(ba)025:490: nyan thos pas gtso cher mkhan po /
NK015(ba)025:491: byang chub sems dpas gtso cher rgyal sras sam /
NK015(ba)025:493: theg chen pas gtso cher rje btsun rin po che ba'am /
NK015(ba)025:495: rig byed spyi'i ming la slob dpon ces zer ro //
NK015(ba)025:496: dama pa ni lta spyod sgom gsum dam pa'i mdzod gsum mam /
NK015(ba)025:497: snying rje dam tshig gnyis dang dam pa'i mdzod lnga ldan pa'i slob dpon khyed ni /
NK015(ba)025:498: badga dang cag ni gzhan ste bdag gzhan rnams kyis
NK015(ba)025:499: rgyud la 'khor ba'i nyes skyon sel bar mdzad pas
NK015(ba)025:501: badga caga rnams kyis rgyud la myang 'das kyi myu
NK015(ba)025:502: gu bskyed par mdzad pas ma dang 'dra ba lagas
NK015(ba)025:503: so // badga caga rnams kyis rgyud la lhag mthong
NK015(ba)025:504: gi ye shes bskyed cing srid zhi'i mtha' las skyob
NK015(ba)025:505: par mdzad pa'i skyabs mgona dang 'dra ba lagsa so
NK015(ba)025:506: so // // badga caga rnams kyi rgyud la thar
NK015(ba)025:507: pa'i lam ston par mdzad pa'i lam ston pa mkhan
NK015(ba)025:509: badga caga rnams ngan song gi 'dam nas drangs zhing
NK015(ba)025:510: sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'dren par mdzad pas sna
NK015(ba)025:512: ma rig pa'i mun khamas sela bar mdzad pa'i phyir sgron me dang 'dra ba lags so //
NK015(ba)025:513: nyon mongs pa dug gsum gyi nad sel bar mdzad pas sman pa dang 'dra ba lagas so /
NK015(ba)025:515: / 'gro ba rnams 'khor ba'i chu bo chen po bzhi
NK015(ba)025:516: las sgrol bar mdzad pa'i phyir grub bo che dang
NK015(ba)025:519: bla ma'i zhal nas theg sgo sna tshogs ston pas
NK015(ba)025:520: nyi ma dang 'dra ba'i zhal la phyag 'tshal lo
NK015(ba)025:521: // sku la sdom gsum gyi nyes pa'i dri ma
NK015(ba)025:522: med pas zla ba dang 'dra ba'i sku la phyag
NK015(ba)025:523: // 'atshala lo // theg sgo sna tshogs gsung pa
NK015(ba)025:524: la log bshad kyi dri ma mi mnga' bas pad+ma
NK015(ba)025:525: dang 'dra ba'i gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:526: mtha' bral gyi chos nyid mngon du gyur pas nama mkha'a dang 'dra ba'i thugsa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:527: bla ma'i yon tan gyis gdul bya'i re ba skong bar mdzad pa de la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:528: phrin lasa kyi 'gro ba kuna myang 'das kyi sa
NK015(ba)025:529: la sgrol bar mdzad pa de la phyag 'tshal lo
NK015(ba)025:530: // dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:531: bla ma desa bskyed pa'i 'das ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum gyi sangsa rgyas dang /
NK015(ba)025:532: dam pa'i chosa rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:533: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa ma lusa pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:534: gsang sngags kyi dge 'dun riga 'dzina dang /
NK015(ba)025:535: mtshan nyid thig chen gyi dge 'dun byang chub semsa dapa'a dang /
NK015(ba)025:536: gnas pa lam stegs la nyan rang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun dang bcas pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:537: yi dam la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:539: dang po zhi ba la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:540: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rgya gzhung zhi ba sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK015(ba)025:541: ma bcos pas de bzhina nyid /
NK015(ba)025:542: der son pas na gshegas pa ste de ltar sangs rgyas sku lnga kun gyi badga po /
NK015(ba)025:543: ye shesa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam ye shes lnga
NK015(ba)025:544: ni rgya mtsho dang 'dra bas raba tu bab pa'o
NK015(ba)025:545: // de yang thugsa rang byung gi ye shes su 'dus so //
NK015(ba)025:546: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam dkyil 'khora 'dul bya yida
NK015(ba)025:547: dang mthun pa bzhina 'byung bas dper na gter mdzod
NK015(ba)025:548: bzhin no // des na kun bzang 'di ni nor
NK015(ba)025:549: bu rin po che dang 'dra bas sangs rgyas thams
NK015(ba)025:550: cad kyi yon tan gyi mdzoda 'dzin cing /
NK015(ba)025:551: yul dang shes pa gnyis su med pa ni rdo rje'i yida te /
NK015(ba)025:552: rtogs ma rtogs gi dbang gis 'khor 'das thams cad
NK015(ba)025:553: kyi byed pa po kun tu bzang po la phyag
NK015(ba)025:554: 'tshal lo // khro bo la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:555: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i khro bo snang ba dam pa
NK015(ba)025:556: rgyan las 'khor 'das thamsa cada kyi ngo bo dbyer
NK015(ba)025:557: med pa ni mnyam pa nyid ste chos sku'o /
NK015(ba)025:559: / 'khor 'das spang blang med par longs spyod pas na bde ba /
NK015(ba)025:560: spyod dus srid zhi gnyis kyi dri mas ma gos pas na chena po ste longs sku /
NK015(ba)025:561: rkang pa'i gzhi ma nges pa las /
NK015(ba)025:562: lag pas gara sna tshogs su bsgyur ba dang 'dra bar /
NK015(ba)025:563: dgongs pa chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK015(ba)025:564: gdul bya log rtog can la gang la gang 'dul
NK015(ba)025:565: gyi sgo nas don mdzad pa ni sprul sku ste
NK015(ba)025:566: / de ltar sku gsum lhun gyi grub pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:567: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las la dabnga bsgyur ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:568: de yang rten byed pa'i ngos nas sku lnga /
NK015(ba)025:569: brda sprod pa'i ngos nas gsung lnga /
NK015(ba)025:570: dgongs pa zab mo'i ngos nas thugsa lnga /
NK015(ba)025:571: lung sgra tshad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba 'chad pa po'i gnyer bya yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:572: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i ngos nas yon tan lnga /
NK015(ba)025:573: bya ba grub pa'i ngos nas phrin las lnga /
NK015(ba)025:574: de dag zad mi shes pas mi zada pa chos sku'i rgyan la gzugs sku che /
NK015(ba)025:575: gzugs sku'i rgyan la chos sku che bas rgyan gyi /
NK015(ba)025:576: 'khor lo ni sku rigs nyer lnga gcig yod pas na kun yod de /
NK015(ba)025:577: dper na 'khor lo'i rtsibs gcig 'ju na kun 'khor ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:578: 'dra bar sku lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas de
NK015(ba)025:579: nyid gdul bya lugs 'byung ldog rnams la khro bor
NK015(ba)025:580: snang ste / he ni dgyes pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:582: rtogs pas bdag don la dgyes pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:583: chos dbyings mngon du rtogs cing /
NK015(ba)025:584: thugs rjes gzhan don la dgyes pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:585: gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis gdul bya la snang ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:586: ru r+aa ga na chags pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:587: rtogs pas bdag don la chags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:588: dgongs pa chos sku las ma g.yos shing /
NK015(ba)025:589: thugs rjes gzhan don la chags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:590: gdul bya'i don byed pa la rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:591: de yang ka ru byas na thugs rje /
NK015(ba)025:593: kar byas na byed pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:594: thugs rje phrin las kyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:595: yang na he ru ka ni khrag 'thung la 'bru gnur ba yang snang ngo //
NK015(ba)025:596: de ltar he ru ka khrag 'thung chen po'i tshogs la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:597: gnyis pa mchod pa'i yan lag la /
NK015(ba)025:599: sgeg mo brgyad mchod gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:601: sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu pa las zug rngu mi mnga'
NK015(ba)025:602: gzhi gnas lugs bde ba chen po'i ngang dera gshegsa
NK015(ba)025:603: so tshogs / bdud bzhi bcoma zhing che ba'i yon tan rnams dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)025:604: rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'adsa pas /
NK015(ba)025:605: mtha' gnyis dang bdud bzhi las rgyal bas rgyal ba /
NK015(ba)025:606: mtha' yas pas rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba /
NK015(ba)025:607: 'das pa ye shesa kyi snang bas bsdus pa thams cad dang /
NK015(ba)025:608: khams gsum mam srid pa gsum po rgya mtsho dang
NK015(ba)025:609: 'dra bas mtha' yasa pa rnams kyi log rtog 'khor
NK015(ba)025:610: ba'i snang ngor shar ba thams cad dang /
NK015(ba)025:611: lam pa'i spyod pa mtha' yas rgya mtsho dang 'dra
NK015(ba)025:612: ba yon tan rmad du byung ba sangs rgyas 'grub
NK015(ba)025:613: pa'i thabs kun kyang kun tu bzang po'i mchoda sprin
NK015(ba)025:614: gyis mchoga tu rola cing ma gyur pa med do
NK015(ba)025:616: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i sngags kyi mgo 'dren /
NK015(ba)025:618: sarba ta th+aa ga to b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)025:619: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'das pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK015(ba)025:620: bi shwa mu khe b+h+yasna tshogs po'i gdug pa can ste /
NK015(ba)025:621: ma 'das pa 'khor ba'i sems can dang /
NK015(ba)025:622: sarba thams cad th+aa kham nam mkha' ut+ga te byas pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:626: kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin /
NK015(ba)025:627: de ci tsa ma na i mam ga ga na kham 'di nam mkha'i khams gang ba /
NK015(ba)025:628: s+w+aa h+aa ni gzhi tshugs par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:629: ces 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos nyid
NK015(ba)025:630: kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin du ma gyur pa
NK015(ba)025:631: med pas / de la phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid dang bzhi'i don bsgom dgos te /
NK015(ba)025:632: de la phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:633: rgya mtsho thams cad yon chab /
NK015(ba)025:634: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad me tog /
NK015(ba)025:635: lho sprin na bun thams cad bdug spos /
NK015(ba)025:636: nyi zla skar gsum ni mar me /
NK015(ba)025:637: chu bo thams cad ni dri chab /
NK015(ba)025:638: ri bo thams cad zhal zas /
NK015(ba)025:639: sgra grags thams cad ni rol mor bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:647: snang ba thams cad mchod pa'i tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:648: sgra grags thams cad rol mo dang mchod pa 'bul
NK015(ba)025:649: ba'i tshig dran rtog thams cad de las mi 'da'
NK015(ba)025:650: bar bsgom pa'i khyer so gsum mam /
NK015(ba)025:653: dran rtog thugs kyi khyer so gsum dang ma bral bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:654: de kho na nyid kyi mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:655: 'khor 'das lam pa'i spyod pa ma lus pa kun
NK015(ba)025:656: bsal bzhag rdul tsam med pa thams cad ma skyes
NK015(ba)025:657: pas kun tu bzang mo'i dang du ro gcig pas
NK015(ba)025:659: de ma 'gags pa 'khor 'das kyi rnam pa mchod pa'i tshogs su cir yang 'char ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:660: kun tu bzang po'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK015(ba)025:661: de gnyis kyang ngo bo la dbyer med pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:662: gnyis su med pa byang chub sems kyi de kho na nyid do //
NK015(ba)025:663: sgeg mo brgyad mchod pa la gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:664: dang po phyi sgeg bzhi ni /
NK015(ba)025:665: rang gi thugs ka nas yi ge gsum 'phros te /
NK015(ba)025:668: h'u gi byin gyis brlabs pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:669: yang na yi ge gsum po 'di /
NK015(ba)025:670: 'bul bya'i yul sku gsung thugs ldan mtshon pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:671: sngon du 'gro ba phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:672: raba tu dga' ba ni mchod pa'i dngos po gang dang gang yin pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:673: de'i badga po mchod pa 'bul ba'i yul la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:674: ces phyag 'tshal don gnyis bsgrub pa mchod pa'i dngos grub zhu ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:675: mchod pa chen po me tog 'di phul bas /
NK015(ba)025:676: dam tshiga chen po nang nas dam pa ni byams
NK015(ba)025:677: pa chen po yin pas de bdag gis rgyud la
NK015(ba)025:678: grub para mdzoda ces smon lam btab /
NK015(ba)025:681: badz+ra rdo rje push+pe me tog grih+na zung /
NK015(ba)025:682: gsang sngags bla med kyi skabs 'dir gnyis med don gyi mchod pa yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:683: rdo rje me tog gi mchod pa 'di zung la ces pa'i don no //
NK015(ba)025:684: h'u bskyed pa'i sa bon yin no //
NK015(ba)025:685: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las h'u ser po 'phros
NK015(ba)025:686: pas me tog bsham zin yong na de la phog
NK015(ba)025:687: med na yid sprul yin pas h'u de yongs su
NK015(ba)025:688: gyur pa las / lha mo me tog ma ser
NK015(ba)025:689: mo me tog bsnams pa dpag tu med pa rnams
NK015(ba)025:690: kyi sku la me tog 'thor bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:692: raba tu dag'a ba'i badga la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:693: mchod pa chen po bdug spos 'di phul bas de
NK015(ba)025:694: bzhina gshegas pa'i dam tshiga ni snying rje chen po
NK015(ba)025:695: yin pas de bdag gi rgyud la grub para mdzoda
NK015(ba)025:696: / badz+ra d+hu pe ni bdug spos /
NK015(ba)025:697: grih+na h'u bdag gi thugs ka nas h'u sngon po
NK015(ba)025:698: 'phros pas lha mo bdug spos ma sngon mos bdug
NK015(ba)025:699: spos bsnams nas shangs la mchod /
NK015(ba)025:701: raba tu badga ba'i badga la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:702: mchod pa chena po mar me 'di phul bas /
NK015(ba)025:703: dag'a ba chen po bdag gi rgyud la grub para mdzoda /
NK015(ba)025:705: grih+na h'u h'u dmar mo las mar me ma dmar mos mar me bsnams nas spyan la mchod /
NK015(ba)025:707: raba tu dag'a ba'i badga la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:708: mchod pa chena po dri chab 'di phul bas /
NK015(ba)025:709: btang snyomsa chen po bdag gi rgyud la grub para mdzoda /
NK015(ba)025:710: badz+ra g+han+d+he ni dri chab grih+na h'u h'u ljang ku
NK015(ba)025:711: las dri chab ma ljang ku dri chab thogs nas
NK015(ba)025:713: nang sgeg bzhi'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:715: h'u bskyed pa'i sa bon ste /
NK015(ba)025:716: bdag gi thugs kha nas h'u dkar mo las /
NK015(ba)025:717: lha mo sgeg mo dkar mo me long bsnams pa byung nas gzugs kyi mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:718: badz+ra m+aa l+ye phreng ba t+r+aam bskyed pa'i sa bon ste /
NK015(ba)025:719: thugs ka nas t+r+aam ser po las lha mo phreng
NK015(ba)025:720: ba ma ser mo phyag na rin po che'i phreng
NK015(ba)025:721: ba bsnams pa byung nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbu
NK015(ba)025:724: h+r+ai bskyed pa'i sa bon ste /
NK015(ba)025:725: thugs ka nas h+r+ai dmar po las lha mo glu
NK015(ba)025:726: ma dmar mo phyag na pi wam bsnams pa byung
NK015(ba)025:729: a bskyed pa'i sa bon ste /
NK015(ba)025:730: thugs ka nas a ljang ku las lha mo gar
NK015(ba)025:731: ma ljang ku phyag na gar gyi pho ru zhal
NK015(ba)025:732: zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa bsnams nas ro'i
NK015(ba)025:734: gsum pa sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:735: sbyang bya sdig pa sgo drug de /
NK015(ba)025:736: sbyang byed gnyen po stobs bzhi yis byang tshul sbyor dngos rjes gsum yis /
NK015(ba)025:737: rang bzhin dag pa sngon du bya //
NK015(ba)025:739: dang po sdig pa'i sgo drug ni /
NK015(ba)025:740: rgyu'i sgo nyon mongs pa dug gsum gyis kun nas bslang ba /
NK015(ba)025:743: yul gyi sgo mkhan slob pha ma man chad /
NK015(ba)025:744: sems can phal ba yan chad /
NK015(ba)025:747: gzhan la byed du bcug pa /
NK015(ba)025:748: gzhan gyi byas pa la rjes su yi rang dang bcas pa /
NK015(ba)025:750: thog ma med pa nas da lta yan chad du sdig pa gang byas pa /
NK015(ba)025:756: kha na ma tho ba gsum /
NK015(ba)025:761: spyir dkon mchog gi rten drung du bshags dgos kyang /
NK015(ba)025:762: 'dir bla ma zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa dpang por bzhugs la /
NK015(ba)025:763: gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i stobs ni /
NK015(ba)025:764: sbyor ba'i dus su bshags sems skye ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:765: dngos gzhi'i dus sdig pa'i dngos po gang byas thams cad do //
NK015(ba)025:767: sdig pa sun phyung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:768: gang zag sun phyung ba gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:769: dang po sdig pa sun phyung ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:770: sdig pa byas pa dug khong du song ba bzhin tu re ma legs bsam pa'i 'gyod pa /
NK015(ba)025:771: gang zag sun phyung ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:772: sdig pa gang byas ngag thog tu brjod cing bshags la /
NK015(ba)025:774: phyin chad srog la bab kyang sdig pa mi byed pa'i dam bca' ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:776: sbyor ba'i dus su sems bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)025:778: dngos gzhi sdig pa bshags pa la /
NK015(ba)025:781: rang gzhan gyi tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas /
NK015(ba)025:782: da lta la thug gi bar du sdig pa mi
NK015(ba)025:783: dge ba ci byas pa la yi rang dang bcas
NK015(ba)025:784: pa / sdom pa gsum gyi chag nyams 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK015(ba)025:785: khyad par du rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig chag nyams thams cad bshags par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:787: gang la 'tshal na bshags pa'i dpang po la 'tshal zhing /
NK015(ba)025:789: badga gi dus tshe raba thoga ma meda pa nasa /
NK015(ba)025:790: tha ma da lta yan chada du mtshams med pa lnga /
NK015(ba)025:795: mi dge ba bcu la sogs pa sdig pa gang spyad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:796: nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyams nas zhiga pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:797: phyi nang gi dama tshig nyamsa pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:798: khyad para du nyon mongas pa che zhing bag meda spyod pa'i dbang dang /
NK015(ba)025:799: le lo'i dbang du song bas /
NK015(ba)025:800: gsang sngags bla med rang gzhung gi dam tshig rtsa ba yana lag la sogas pa'i bsrung bya rnams /
NK015(ba)025:801: sngar dbang bskur ba'i skabs su dam bca' zhing 'dir bsrung ma thub nas /
NK015(ba)025:802: zhig ste rtsa ba nas nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:803: sna re zhig nas rala la /
NK015(ba)025:804: sna 'ga' re zhig nas nyamsa pa /
NK015(ba)025:805: shes bzhin du khyad du basda nas yala bar dora bas dam las log pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:806: de ltar bsrung bya gzhunga du ma snyigsa pas spyod pa snyoms las byas pas /
NK015(ba)025:807: res bsrung bya gzhung dang 'agla tshabs che /
NK015(ba)025:808: res 'gal tshabs chung ba rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:809: nyamsa pa can dang 'grogs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:811: ma tshora bar nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:812: nyamsa so 'atshala ni nyams tshod tsam red bsam pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:813: gzhan yang rtsa ba yana lag gi dam tshig grogs ngan pa'i zla la nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:814: rang gi zhar la nyams shor ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:815: dran dang shes bzhin dang mi ldan dus kun tu
NK015(ba)025:816: nyamas pa rnams sems gnong zhing ngag 'gyod pa'i sgo
NK015(ba)025:817: nas bshagsa pasa / badga la gang gi dam tshig sdom pa rnams tshangas pa stsol cig /
NK015(ba)025:818: shina tu ngag gi 'gyod cinga sems kyi gdung ba'i sgo nas bashagas para bagyi'o //
NK015(ba)025:819: rjes ni de ltar bshags pa la yid rang zhing /
NK015(ba)025:820: phyin chad srog la bab kyang sdig pa mi byed par dam bca' la /
NK015(ba)025:821: rgyal ba rnams kyis kyang bdag la sdig pa dag pa'i gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK015(ba)025:822: sdig pa la dge ba med kyang bshags na dag nas dge ba yod pas /
NK015(ba)025:823: ci thub bshags pa la 'bad dgos so //
NK015(ba)025:824: sdig pa dag pa sngon du 'gro ba'i rgyu ni /
NK015(ba)025:826: byin rlabs kun gyis gegs gyur pa /
NK015(ba)025:827: sgrib pa rnam gnyis yin pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:828: de dag byang ba rab tu gces //
NK015(ba)025:830: bzhi pa rjes su yi rang ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:831: dge ba'i nang nas rjes su yi rang mchog /
NK015(ba)025:833: gzhan gyis dge ba gang byed la rjes su yi rang bsgom dgos te /
NK015(ba)025:834: gang dang gang gi dge ba la rjes su yi rang bsgom na /
NK015(ba)025:835: yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangsa rgyas dang /
NK015(ba)025:836: sa dang lam la gnas pa'i byang chub semsa dapa'a
NK015(ba)025:837: thams cad kyi 'gro don brlab po che mdzad pa
NK015(ba)025:838: dang 'aphagas pa nyan rang rnams kyis zhi bde snyoms
NK015(ba)025:839: 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:840: so so'i skye bo'i dge ba'i rtsa ba gang basgas pa ma lus thams cad dang /
NK015(ba)025:841: de dag gis dge ba gang bsags pa thams cad
NK015(ba)025:842: la dus rtag tu badga ni rjes su yi ranga
NK015(ba)025:843: ngo // lnga pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:844: sangs rgyas gsar bu 'gro don ma mdzad pa rnams
NK015(ba)025:845: la gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa
NK015(ba)025:846: re re phul nas chos 'khor bskor bar zhu ba
NK015(ba)025:848: 'bras bu mngona du gyur pa ringa pora ma lona
NK015(ba)025:849: pa'i sangs rgyas gsar bu rnams phyogsa bcu'i 'jiga rten
NK015(ba)025:850: gyi khamsa na bzhugas so 'atshala thams cad la /
NK015(ba)025:851: 'gro ba sems can rnams myur du bla na med
NK015(ba)025:852: pa'i byang chub thob pa'i slad du bla na meda
NK015(ba)025:853: pa theg pa chen po'i chosa kyi 'khora lo bskora
NK015(ba)025:854: bar bskul lo // drug pa mya ngan mi 'da' bar bzhugs su gsol ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:855: sangs rgyas 'gro don rdzogs nas mya ngan las 'da'
NK015(ba)025:856: bar bzhed pa rnams la pad+ma 'dab ma stong ldan
NK015(ba)025:857: re re gdan du 'bul nas 'khor ba ma stong
NK015(ba)025:858: gi bar du sems can gyi don mdzad pa zhu
NK015(ba)025:860: gdul bya'i don bya ba tshar ba'i thub pa sangs rgyas rnams kyis /
NK015(ba)025:861: dgongsa pa chos kyi dbyingsa su mya ngan las 'ad'a
NK015(ba)025:862: bar bzheda pa rnams ji srid 'khora ba stong para
NK015(ba)025:864: bzhugs nas mya ngan mi 'da' bar gsola ba 'debas so //
NK015(ba)025:865: bdun pa bsngo ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:866: bdag gzhan sems can thams cad sangs rgyas thob pa'i ched du /
NK015(ba)025:867: rang gzhan gyis dus gsum bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa
NK015(ba)025:868: ba bla na med pa'i byang chub chen po'i sar
NK015(ba)025:871: badga gi tshe rabas dus thoga ma meda pa nasa /
NK015(ba)025:872: da lta yana chada du dge ba ci spyad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:874: phyag 'tshal mchod pa 'bul sdig pa bshags dge ba
NK015(ba)025:875: la rjes su yi rang ba chos kyi 'khor lo
NK015(ba)025:876: bskor nas bskul ba mya ngan mi 'da' bar gsol
NK015(ba)025:877: ba btab pa'i dge ba ci spyan pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:878: de rnams kyi mthu nus pa la brten nas badga
NK015(ba)025:879: dang gazhana sems can thams cad sangs rgyas thob pa'i
NK015(ba)025:880: dona du bla na med pa byang chub chen po'i
NK015(ba)025:882: brgyad pa dam bca' smon lam gyi yan lag la gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:883: dang po dam bca' ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:885: rdo rje rtse gcig phyag rgya'i //
NK015(ba)025:886: dam baca'i sdom pa gzhung bzhin snyeg /
NK015(ba)025:888: rdo rje rtse gcig phyag rgya bca' la /
NK015(ba)025:889: sngar dbang zhu ba'i dus su dam bcas pa la zhig ral byung ba rnams /
NK015(ba)025:890: 'dir dpang po'i spyan sngar dam tshig slar blang ste /
NK015(ba)025:891: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig rnams rang gi srog la bab kyang bsrung bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:893: bla med byang chub sems kyi dam tshig bskyed rdzogs mi spang pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:894: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon drug bkur ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:896: phyag rgya bzhi bsgom pa rgyun mi bacada pa gsung gi dam tshig go //
NK015(ba)025:897: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugas pa'i mched la byamsa pa bskyed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:898: gasnga ba bcu po ni gzhan dona du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK015(ba)025:899: gzhan la smra bar mi bya ba ni thugs kyi dam tshig ste /
NK015(ba)025:900: de lnga ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig /
NK015(ba)025:901: gati mug 'doda chagas dang zhe sdang che /
NK015(ba)025:902: nga rgyal phrag doga ste yang dag pa'i dug lnga
NK015(ba)025:903: sngags kyi lta spyod dang chos mthun du yod pa
NK015(ba)025:904: dang / log pa'i dug lnga lta ba'i rtsis zin na ye shes lnga yin pas mi spanga ngo //
NK015(ba)025:907: dri chen dri chu sha chena /
NK015(ba)025:908: 'di lnga la grub pa bzhi'i rgyan pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)025:909: yang daga pa'i snod bcud 'di dag longs spyod par byas te mi dora ro //
NK015(ba)025:910: de bcu ni yan lag gi dam tshig go //
NK015(ba)025:911: smon lam ni bde bar gshegsa pa rgyal ba zhi
NK015(ba)025:912: khro khyed ci 'dra ba'i zhing khams gdul bya tshad
NK015(ba)025:913: med mnga' ba de 'dra kho nara badga kyang 'grub
NK015(ba)025:914: par gyur ciga / smon lam de 'agrub pa'i rgyu
NK015(ba)025:915: la lam gyis chos spyod pa rmada byung bsam yasa
NK015(ba)025:916: pa kun 'gro ba sems can la phana pa'i dona
NK015(ba)025:918: mdor na byang chub sems dpa' spyod mchog dam pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:919: sngags kyi sku gsung thugsa kyi phyag rgya 'di nyid /
NK015(ba)025:920: bdag gi srog gi phyir yanga mi gtong na /
NK015(ba)025:921: de bas rdo rje rgyal po khyod kyi byin gyis rlobsa shig /
NK015(ba)025:923: sangsa rgyas kyi sems can gyi don madzada par daka'a
NK015(ba)025:924: ba rnams kyang bdag gisa madzada byang chub sems dpa'i
NK015(ba)025:925: mgo dang rkang lag byin nas spyad daka'a ba rnams
NK015(ba)025:927: de bas gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa rnal 'byor
NK015(ba)025:928: chen po zhi khro'i dkyil 'khora bsgom pa'i skabs 'dira
NK015(ba)025:929: badga cag gi bsam pa'i 'bras bu thams cad 'grub
NK015(ba)025:930: par gyur cig / h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:931: rang gi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis dpang po'i lha rnams 'od du zhu nas /
NK015(ba)025:932: bdag gi spyi bo nas mar thim /
NK015(ba)025:933: lus ngag yid gsum gyis sdig sgrib thams cad mar 'og sgo dang /
NK015(ba)025:934: sor mo bcu nas mar bud nas /
NK015(ba)025:935: rang gi lus ye shes kyi bdud rtsis gang bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:937: rgyun bshags yan lag brgyad pa rdzogs so //
NK015(ba)025:938: gnyis pa zhi khro'i bshags pa la /
NK015(ba)025:942: snying po bzlas pa'i bshags pa'i yan lag dang lnga las /
NK015(ba)025:943: dang po dgongs su gsol ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:944: bcoma ldan 'adsa zhi khro raba 'byamsa kyi tshogsa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:946: ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba'i tshig ste /
NK015(ba)025:947: gang la ngo mtshar na phyogsa bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal
NK015(ba)025:948: ba kun gyi badga nyida chen po rtsa ba dang
NK015(ba)025:949: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:950: rgyal ba zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK015(ba)025:951: khro bo che mchog dpal dgu yongas rdzogsa dgongsa mdzod /
NK015(ba)025:952: gnas 'dira gshegas la nyi zla pad+ma'i gadna la bzhugas /
NK015(ba)025:954: rang gi mdun du pad+ma'i sdong po la smin mtshams
NK015(ba)025:955: kyi thad du pad 'dab brgyad du gyes pa'i 'dab
NK015(ba)025:956: ma brgyad lte ba dang dgu la nyi zla phrug
NK015(ba)025:958: de'i dbus su che mchog yon tan gyi lha tshogs byon nas bzhugs par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:962: byang du phur pa phrin las /
NK015(ba)025:963: shar lhor ma mo rbod gtong /
NK015(ba)025:964: lho nub tu bla ma rig 'dzin /
NK015(ba)025:965: nub byang du 'jig rten mchod bstod /
NK015(ba)025:966: byang shar du dmod pa drag sngags /
NK015(ba)025:967: che mchog gi dbu thog tu zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK015(ba)025:968: zhi ba gtso bo'i dbu thog tu rtsa ba'i bla
NK015(ba)025:969: ma rdo rje 'chang gi cha byad can la brgyud
NK015(ba)025:970: pa'i bla mas bskor ba dang bcas pa byon nas
NK015(ba)025:971: bzhugs par bsams pa'i mdun du /
NK015(ba)025:972: sdom pa gsum gyis nyams chaga na raga ngan song du skye ba'i rgyu sbyang ba'i phyir phyag dang /
NK015(ba)025:973: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchoda pa bzhes su gsol /
NK015(ba)025:974: ces mchod pa dpag tu med pas mchod par dmigs so //
NK015(ba)025:975: gnyis pa phyag 'tshal ba'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:976: rang gi lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul nas
NK015(ba)025:977: mgo bos zhabs la btud pas phyag 'tshal bar bsam
NK015(ba)025:978: la / snyan pa rgyud gdams ngag gi gnad ma chug pa /
NK015(ba)025:979: byin rlabs nyams rtogs kyi drod ma yal ba /
NK015(ba)025:980: bla ma brgyud pa'i zam ma chad pa /
NK015(ba)025:981: dbang bzhi'i chu rgyun ma nub pa sogs yona tan
NK015(ba)025:982: phun gsum tshogsa pa mnga' ba bla ma rnams la
NK015(ba)025:984: 'khor 'das phyogs gcig tu dmigas su meda cing spros
NK015(ba)025:985: pa'i mtha' brgyad dam bzhi dang bral ba'i chos kyi
NK015(ba)025:987: snang stong dbyer med bde ba chena po longsa spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK015(ba)025:989: / 'gro ba sems can gyi mgona skyabs dang dpung gnyen
NK015(ba)025:990: gang 'dul thabs kyi sgo nas cir yanga sprul pa'i
NK015(ba)025:992: cir yang sprul dus dgongs pa gnas lugsa mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)025:993: ba skye 'jig dang bral ba la ma g.yos pas
NK015(ba)025:994: rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:995: yang daga pa'i don sku gsum lhun grub rang rig
NK015(ba)025:996: pa'i mngon gsum du snang ba mngona para byang chub
NK015(ba)025:998: nyon mongas rnam rtog zhi bar madzada pa'i zhi ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:999: bdud ru tra la sogs log par lta ba rnams
NK015(ba)025:1000: tshar gcoda par mdzad pa'i khro bo'i sku la phyag
NK015(ba)025:1001: 'atshala lo // thabsa mkhas pa'i sgo nas skye 'gro
NK015(ba)025:1002: rnams kyi tshe srog gi bdag po ni gshin rje
NK015(ba)025:1003: 'atshala lo // yin / de'i gshed du gyur pas
NK015(ba)025:1004: sems can gyi dpal mgon du gyur pa sku la
NK015(ba)025:1005: 'gyur ba mi mnga' bas tshe badag 'jam dapala sku
NK015(ba)025:1007: nyes pa'i skyon dang bral zhing gsung 'gag pa med
NK015(ba)025:1008: pas theg sgo sna tshogs kyi sgra sgrogas kyang nyes
NK015(ba)025:1009: skyon gyis ma gos pas pad+ma'i gsung la phyag 'atshala
NK015(ba)025:1010: lo // thugs 'khrul pa med pa yang dag pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1011: chos nyid kyis dona dang ldan pas badz+ra'i thugsa la
NK015(ba)025:1012: lo // phyag 'atshala lo // yon tan gyi nyon
NK015(ba)025:1013: mongs pa duga lnga'i nad sela bar byed pas bdud
NK015(ba)025:1015: phrin las kyi dregas pa can thams cad 'jomas par madzada pa phur pa'i lha la phyag 'atshala lo /
NK015(ba)025:1017: / 'byung ba'i mang'a badga ma mo'i tshogas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)025:1018: sa dang lam yongs su rdzogsa par mdzad pa'i riga 'dzina tshogsa la phyag 'atshala lo //
NK015(ba)025:1019: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung bar madzada pa'i dam
NK015(ba)025:1020: can sde dpon sum cu po rnams la phyag 'atshala
NK015(ba)025:1021: lo // sdang byed kyi dgra gnod byed kyi bgegsa
NK015(ba)025:1022: bar du gcod pa'i bduda rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1023: sngagsa badga dregs pa'i sde dpon bco brgyad po rnams
NK015(ba)025:1025: gsum pa phan yon gyi yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:1026: sems can ganga gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i /
NK015(ba)025:1027: dkyil 'khora lha tshogs rnams kyi mtshan thos phyag matshala na /
NK015(ba)025:1028: dam tshig chaga nyamsa ma lusa pa kuna byang nas dag na /
NK015(ba)025:1029: mtshamsa med lnga'i las byas pa dag pa la smos ci dgosa ste dag par 'gyur la /
NK015(ba)025:1030: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan thos na na raka
NK015(ba)025:1031: ngan song gsum gyi gansa na 'dug pa rnams kyang
NK015(ba)025:1033: 'o na ngan song du thar bar mtho ris su skye'am zhe na /
NK015(ba)025:1034: riga 'dzina thob nas rgyal ba'i zhing du gragsa te sangs rgyas so //
NK015(ba)025:1035: bzhi pa snying po bzlas pa'i yan lag ni /
NK015(ba)025:1036: rdo rje semas dpa'i gsang sngags yi ge brgya pa dngosa 'di bzlas na /
NK015(ba)025:1037: las ngan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1038: dam tshig chag nyamsa kyi sgrib pa thams cad daga par byed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1039: 'khora ba donga nas sprug par byed pa'i yanga snying 'di bzla'o //
NK015(ba)025:1040: de yang rang gi spyi bor pad zla nyi ma gsum brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1041: rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig
NK015(ba)025:1042: phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu thugs kar
NK015(ba)025:1044: zhabs g.yas kyi mthe bong spyi gtsug du reg pa /
NK015(ba)025:1045: ral pa thor tshug gyen du bcing pa lhag ma
NK015(ba)025:1046: thur du grol ba rin po che'i srog zhu gsol
NK015(ba)025:1047: ba / spyi bor zla ba'i steng du dkar po /
NK015(ba)025:1048: mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du +aahdamara po /
NK015(ba)025:1049: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje dkar po
NK015(ba)025:1050: rtse lnga pa'i lte bar h'u dkar po rdul chu'i
NK015(ba)025:1051: mdog lta bu dkar rtse re de la yi ge
NK015(ba)025:1052: brgya pa kha dog dkar pos g.yas su 'khor ba
NK015(ba)025:1053: / yig 'bru gsum la 'od byung nas bdag gi
NK015(ba)025:1054: lus ngag yid gsum la phog pas chag nyams sdig
NK015(ba)025:1055: sgrib thams cad dag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1056: gzhan yang 'og gi yi ge brgya pa bzla ba'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:1057: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka'i yi ge brgya pa las bdud rtsi byung /
NK015(ba)025:1058: rkang pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong nas bdag gi tshang bug du mar thim /
NK015(ba)025:1059: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib thams cad rkang
NK015(ba)025:1060: mthil dang sen brags rnams nas mar 'od nag po'i
NK015(ba)025:1062: rang gi lus kyang shel phyis pa ltar dkar sang gyis song bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1063: dpang po rnams kyi thugs ka nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun byung nas sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1065: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa lnga byung nas rang gi gnas lngar thim par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1067: badz+ra sat+wa sa ma ya ni rdo rje sems dpa'i dam tshig /
NK015(ba)025:1068: ma nu pa la ya ni rjes su skyongs shig /
NK015(ba)025:1069: badz+ra sa t+wa ti no pa tish+tha ni rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyis nye bar zhugs shig /
NK015(ba)025:1070: dri d+ho me b+ha wa ni bdag la brten par gyur cig pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1071: su posh+yo mi b+ha wa ni bdag la rgyas par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1072: su to sh+yo me b+ha wa ni bdag la shin du dgyes par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1073: a nu rak+to me b+ha wa ni bdag la rjes su chags par gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1074: sarba sid+d+hi m+me pra yats+tsha ni dngos grub thams cad bdag la rab tu stsol /
NK015(ba)025:1075: sarba karma su tsa me ni bdag la las thams cad rtsol par mdzod cig /
NK015(ba)025:1076: tsit+tam sh+re yahku ru ni sems kyi dpal du mdzod cig /
NK015(ba)025:1077: h'u ni bzhugs pa'i sa bon yin /
NK015(ba)025:1078: ha ha ha ha ni ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1079: ho ni mnyes shing dbang du gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1080: b+ha ga w+aana ni bcom ldan 'das /
NK015(ba)025:1081: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK015(ba)025:1082: badz+ra m+aa me muny+tsa ni rdo rjes bdag rab tu grol bar mdzod cig /
NK015(ba)025:1083: badz+r+ai b+ha wa ni rdo rje can du gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1084: ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+wa +aahdama tshig chen po'i sems dpa' zhes pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1085: lnga pa bshags pa'i yan lag la /
NK015(ba)025:1087: don dam bshags pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:1088: dang po kun rdzob bshags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1089: dpang po'i mdun du lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul nas ngag bshags tshig /
NK015(ba)025:1090: yid 'gyod sems dang bcas pas bshags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1092: bshags sems skyes nas bshags pa la dga' ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:1093: bde gshegas rgyal ba zhi khro yongsa rdzogas rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma dang bcas pa rnams kyi /
NK015(ba)025:1097: snyan gyis gsan du gsola bya ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:1098: bdag gis rgyal ba'i bka'a nas ci ltar 'byung ba bzhin ma spyod pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1099: bla ma'i zhal nas lung ci ltar 'bog pa bzhina
NK015(ba)025:1100: du ma spyad pa'i thog nas slob dpona smad pa
NK015(ba)025:1101: dang / gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i sgor zhugs pa'i mched dang lcam dral ming sring la /
NK015(ba)025:1102: lta loga ni log lta byed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1104: tshig ngag tu smra ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1106: gtsogsa pa ni mgo dang rkang lag bcag pa la sogs /
NK015(ba)025:1107: gnoda pa dngosa su spyad pa ni sku'i dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1108: yi dam gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya dang /
NK015(ba)025:1109: de'i dkyil 'khora bsgom pa rang gi nyamsa su ma gasla ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1110: sngags kyi dzapa bzlas ma daga nas lhag chad dang /
NK015(ba)025:1112: sgra nyamsa pa ste gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1114: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa rnams smras pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1115: gzhan yang spyir gsang ba bzhi /
NK015(ba)025:1117: gang gi gsang bar 'os pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1118: gnyer gtan gnyis dang gasnga ba bcu po gzhan la
NK015(ba)025:1119: sgragsa cing bla ma bslu ba ste thugs kyi dam
NK015(ba)025:1120: tshig go // de ltar sku gsung thugs rtsa ba dam tshig nyamsa pa mthola zhing bshagsa so //
NK015(ba)025:1121: sbyor sgrol ma byin len pa dang ngag barlinga po rdzun du smra ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:1122: spyad para bya ba'i dama tshiga lnga /
NK015(ba)025:1123: shesa bya lnga dang bsgrub bya lnga /
NK015(ba)025:1124: mi spanga lnga dang dang blang lnga ste /
NK015(ba)025:1125: khyad par yan lag gi dama tshig nyamsa pa mthola zhing bashagas so //
NK015(ba)025:1126: gzhan yang bsnyen pa dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1127: bsgrub pa dang bsgrub pa chen po'i tinga nge 'dzina gyi dam tshig g.yela zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1128: nya dang gnam stong la sogs dusa bzang drug gi
NK015(ba)025:1129: dusa su mchoda pa ma byas nas chagas pa dang
NK015(ba)025:1130: / tshe phyi ma'i chos phyogs le lo chen po dang /
NK015(ba)025:1131: 'jig rten 'di ched du gnyer nas nor rdzas la bsogas 'joga byas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1132: tshogas kyi sbyang ku byas pa ni rje btsun ma'i
NK015(ba)025:1133: tshogs mchod kyi nang nas sngar tshogs gral du ma
NK015(ba)025:1134: 'dug shing dkyil chog ma bsgom par tshogs sprum 'ong
NK015(ba)025:1136: gzhan yang phud la bzhag cing lhag ma la 'phri
NK015(ba)025:1137: bar byas nas phud nyamsa shing kha tshar shor ba
NK015(ba)025:1139: de ltar tshora ba dang ma tshor ba'i rkyen dbang
NK015(ba)025:1140: gisa lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo gsum bag meda
NK015(ba)025:1141: pas dama tshig nyamas pa thams cad bashagas so //
NK015(ba)025:1142: don dam pa'i bshags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1143: yid kyi dama tshig nyamas pa lta basa bashagas dgos ste /
NK015(ba)025:1144: de yang 'khor 'das kun gyi gzhi byang chub kyi semas snang stong dbyer med du gnas pas /
NK015(ba)025:1145: de bas snang ba kun rdzob kyis phyogs su ma
NK015(ba)025:1146: chad pa yina pa med ste stong dus snang ba'i
NK015(ba)025:1147: rtsis kyis zin pa'i lta ba rtogsa cing /
NK015(ba)025:1148: stong pa don dam gyi phyogs su rgya ma chad
NK015(ba)025:1149: pa min te stong pa nyid sna tshogs su shar
NK015(ba)025:1150: ba mina pa meda pa'i dgongas pa nyams su lona
NK015(ba)025:1151: nas sgom pas yin pa'i lta ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1152: min pa meda pa'i sgom pa gnyis ya ma bral bar khyer ba'i spyod pa rtogsa pasa /
NK015(ba)025:1153: 'bras bu thob du re ba mi thob du dogas
NK015(ba)025:1154: pa meda pa'i gzhi don byang chub semsa de mngon
NK015(ba)025:1156: de ltar du rtogs pas rtsa ba dang yana lag
NK015(ba)025:1157: thamsa cada kyis dam tshig chaga nyamsa dang por ma
NK015(ba)025:1158: byung bar du ma skyes pasa /
NK015(ba)025:1159: bashagas bya'i yul dang bshagsa byed kyi mkhan po gnyis su meda pa grol ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:1162: na rag dong sprug dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud du /
NK015(ba)025:1163: kun bzang che mchog gis gsungs pa rdzogs so //
NK015(ba)025:1164: gsum pa man+da la 'bul ba la gnyis te /
NK015(ba)025:1176: yon tan la sogs pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:1177: de rnams zhib par zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:1181: sprul sku zhing gi man+dala dang gsum yod pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1182: chos sku zhing gi man+dala ni logs su shes la /
NK015(ba)025:1187: dang po longs sku zhing gi man+dala la yang /
NK015(ba)025:1188: bsgrub pa zhing gi man+dala dang /
NK015(ba)025:1189: mchod pa zhing gi man+dala gnyis khas /
NK015(ba)025:1191: rang yi dam du gsal ba'i smin mtshams nas yi
NK015(ba)025:1192: ge b+h+r+aum gcig spros pa 'od du zhu ba las
NK015(ba)025:1196: mig mang ris su bris la /
NK015(ba)025:1197: rgya mdo thams cad rin po che'i tshom bus spras pa /
NK015(ba)025:1198: mig gi bltar mi bzod pa'i 'od dang ldan pa'i dbus su /
NK015(ba)025:1199: rin po che'i khri seng ge brgyad kyis nye bar btegs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1200: rin po che'i mdzod mig bdun bdun dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)025:1201: gdung ma zung sgril du 'khor ba /
NK015(ba)025:1202: rin po che'i d+r+wa bas khri kheb byas pa /
NK015(ba)025:1203: de'i steng du pad zla nyi ma gsum brtsegs kyi
NK015(ba)025:1204: steng du rtsa ba'i bla ma la brgyud pa'i bla
NK015(ba)025:1206: de'i shar phyogs su glang po che brgyad kyis btegs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1207: yi dam lha tshogs rnams la chos skyong ba'i srung mas bskor ba /
NK015(ba)025:1208: g.yas su rta mchog brgyad kyi btegs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1209: sangs rgyas dkon mchog sku gsum gyi bsdus pa rnams bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1210: rgyab tu rma bya brgyad kyis btegs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1211: chos dkon mchog rgyu 'bras lam gsum gyi bsdus pa
NK015(ba)025:1212: rnams gser gyi shog gu la beed+aur+ya'i zhun mas rang
NK015(ba)025:1213: nan du phris pa'i glegs bam rang sgra grags pa
NK015(ba)025:1214: rnams bsam / g.yon du shang shang brgyad kyis btegs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1215: dge 'dun dkon mchog rig pa 'dzin pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1217: byang chub sems dpa' zag pa med pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1218: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1219: gzhan yang sa dang lam la gnas pa rnams bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1220: mchod pa zhing gi man+dala ni /
NK015(ba)025:1221: de dag gi mnga' ris dang spyan lam du /
NK015(ba)025:1222: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad nam mkha' la sprin bzhin du 'byung ba /
NK015(ba)025:1223: bar snang la char bzhin du 'bab pa /
NK015(ba)025:1224: sa gzhi la rtsi shing bzhin du skyes pa /
NK015(ba)025:1225: 'dod dgu thams cad 'byung ba'i sa gzhi /
NK015(ba)025:1226: chos kyi dbyings kyi khyab tshad dang mnyam pa /
NK015(ba)025:1227: bla ma dang dkon mchog la 'bul bar bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1228: mnyes par byed pas mchoda pa /
NK015(ba)025:1229: snang grags mchod pa'i rdzas su mi 'da' bas phyag
NK015(ba)025:1230: rgya mchod pa gzhan pas khyad par du gyur pa
NK015(ba)025:1232: semsa kyi cho 'phrul yid bzhina gyis nor bu lta
NK015(ba)025:1233: bu mchod sprin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshogsa kyi
NK015(ba)025:1234: mchod par bya'o // de yang bdag gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum phyogsa bcur 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:1235: sa gzhi thamsa cad la phog pas sangas rgyas kyis zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK015(ba)025:1236: mnyena zhing 'ajama la rega na shin tu bde ba
NK015(ba)025:1237: dang ldan pa'i 'og gzhi sna tshogas pa'i rina po
NK015(ba)025:1238: che'i sa gzhi mnan na nems pa /
NK015(ba)025:1240: mdzes para byed pa'i ring migs mang ris su bris
NK015(ba)025:1241: zhing sna tshogs rin po che du mas spras pa
NK015(ba)025:1242: dang / t+r+aam 'phros pas ri thams cad la phog
NK015(ba)025:1243: pas yon tan kun 'byunga ba'i nor bu rin chen
NK015(ba)025:1245: ahsprosa pas chu thams cad la phog pas dbyibsa legas
NK015(ba)025:1246: pa'i rdzinga bu bang rim gsum sgo dang ldan pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1247: nang du ro bro ba'i mchog tu gyur pa bsila
NK015(ba)025:1248: zing / dwangs ba'i chu yan lag brgyad ldan du bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1249: b+h+r+aum spros pas khang khyim sgra gur thams cad la
NK015(ba)025:1250: phog pas rin chena gyis khang pa sna tshogsa par
NK015(ba)025:1251: bsam pa dang / t+r+aam 'phros pas nags tshal thams
NK015(ba)025:1252: cad la phog pas phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rin
NK015(ba)025:1254: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad dapaga bsam gyis ljon shing rgyas pa'i tshal du bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1255: h+r+aih'aphrosa pas sgra grags thams cad la phog pas sangs
NK015(ba)025:1256: rgyas byang chub sems dpa' rnams la bstod pa'i glu
NK015(ba)025:1257: dbyangs dang sems can rnams la chos ston pa'i tshigsa
NK015(ba)025:1259: m+aam spros pas sprin dang na bun thams cad la phog pas lhab lhub sna tshogs dang /
NK015(ba)025:1260: bla bre rgyal matshana lha'i na baza'a dang gdugsa su bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1261: t+r+aam 'phros nas skye 'gro rnams kyis rgyan thams cad la phog pas /
NK015(ba)025:1262: rin po che'i do shal dang dpung rgyan dang se mo do ru bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1263: bam a spros pas longs spyod thams cad la phog pas /
NK015(ba)025:1264: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin baza'a ba dang btunga ba dang ro bro ba'i mchog sna tshogs pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1265: trihsprosa pas skye 'gro thams cad la phog pas 'gro
NK015(ba)025:1266: ba thams cad kyang ranga la mdzesa par brgyan pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1267: / mchod rdzas 'dod yon sna tshogs thogs pa'i lha
NK015(ba)025:1268: dang lha mo re re yang grangs rdul snyed rnams
NK015(ba)025:1269: / kyis / rkang pas bro dang lag pas gara la sogas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1270: kha nas skye ba med pa'i glu blang zhing bde
NK015(ba)025:1271: bar gshegs pa rnams la tshigs su bcad pa'i bstod
NK015(ba)025:1273: mang nyung gi tshad phyogsa bcu nam mkha'a yi khamas
NK015(ba)025:1274: khengs par bakanga nasa sngar spyan drang ba'i dkyil 'khora
NK015(ba)025:1276: de ni gsang sngags bla med lugs kyi skye med kyi ngang nas 'gag med kyi rtsal sbyang /
NK015(ba)025:1277: gnyis med du rang grol nas tshe gcig sangs rgyas
NK015(ba)025:1278: thob pa'i thabs lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod
NK015(ba)025:1279: pa'o // sprul sku dag pa zhig gi man+dala ni
NK015(ba)025:1280: thugs ka nas t+r+aam gcig spros pa 'od du zhu
NK015(ba)025:1281: pa'o // ba las / mtha'i rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus su gling bzhi gling phran brgyad ni /
NK015(ba)025:1285: rnga yab dang rnga yab gzhan /
NK015(ba)025:1291: de'i dkyil du ri bo mchog rab /
NK015(ba)025:1297: rol pa'i mtsho bdun gyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)025:1298: ri rab kyis khar rgyal srid rina chena bdun dang /
NK015(ba)025:1299: gter chen po'i bum pa dang ldan zhing dapaga bsam gyis shing dang khrus kyi rdzing bu'i mdzesa pa /
NK015(ba)025:1300: gling bzhi yang lasa bzhi'i dbyibs su yod pa yang /
NK015(ba)025:1306: snang gsal gyi nyi zla gza' skar /
NK015(ba)025:1307: mtha'i lcags ri mu khyud dang bcas par byin gyis
NK015(ba)025:1308: brlab pa'i khyad para lasa steng sum cu rtsa gsum
NK015(ba)025:1310: khong seng lha ma yin gyi rten longs spyod /
NK015(ba)025:1312: phyi rol rgya chen rigs bzhi'i rten longs spyod /
NK015(ba)025:1313: gling bzhi mi'i rten longas spyod phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa rnams /
NK015(ba)025:1314: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzina gyi sgo nas bla ma
NK015(ba)025:1315: dang dkon mchog gsum la 'bul gyis mchoda par bzhes
NK015(ba)025:1316: su gsol / phul ba'i yon tan ni /
NK015(ba)025:1317: 'di ltar du snang ba rgyu lam gyis chosa rnams
NK015(ba)025:1318: thamsa cada 'bras bu'i ngo bor yongas su rdzogas dgos
NK015(ba)025:1319: pa'i phyir sangas rgyas rnams la man+dala 'di phul bas
NK015(ba)025:1320: bsod nams kyis 'bras bu 'aphagas pa'i nor sku gsung
NK015(ba)025:1321: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dbyings ye shes gnyis
NK015(ba)025:1322: dang bdun lhun gyis grub nasa ting nge 'dzina gyi
NK015(ba)025:1323: sgo 'bum phrag rnams la dabnga bsgyur shoga /
NK015(ba)025:1325: na mo phyogas bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhina gshegsa pa
NK015(ba)025:1326: thamsa cada kyi sku dang gsunga dang yon tan dang
NK015(ba)025:1327: phrin lasa dang zhing khamas zaga pa meda pa zada
NK015(ba)025:1328: mi shesa pa rgyan gyi 'khora lo nyer lnga'i bdena
NK015(ba)025:1329: pa dang / rgyal ba rgya mtsho rigs lnga yab
NK015(ba)025:1330: lnga gasnga ba rgya mtsho yum lnga smin pa rgya
NK015(ba)025:1331: mtsho sems dpa' dang sems ma /
NK015(ba)025:1332: gzhan yang brgyud pa'i bla ma rin po chena rnams kyis byin rlabs kyis /
NK015(ba)025:1333: bdag ming ch+gee 'di zhesa bgyi bas semas can thamsa cada kyis dona du /
NK015(ba)025:1334: rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK015(ba)025:1335: dona rang byung gi ye shesa de kho na nyid
NK015(ba)025:1336: kyi dona gyis mnyam bzhag la gang ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1337: rjes thob la shin tu gang ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1338: de bzhin du rdzogs pa chen po'i don gyis mnyam bzhag la rgyas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1339: rjes thob la shin tu rgyas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1340: de bzhin du rdzogs pa chen po'i don gyis bdag gi rgyud /
NK015(ba)025:1341: mnyam bzhag la smin pa dang rjes thob la shin tu smin pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1342: rdzogs pa chen po'i don gyis bdag nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba mtha' dag /
NK015(ba)025:1343: mnyam bzhag la grol ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1344: rjes thob la shina tu grol ba rgya chen po sangs rgyas par madzada du gsola /
NK015(ba)025:1346: yang na gong gi de dag rdzogs chen gyi sa
NK015(ba)025:1347: lam rim gyi pa'i bgrong tshul ltar dga' rab rdo
NK015(ba)025:1348: rje'i nyams rim bzhi pa dang bstun na /
NK015(ba)025:1349: dang po gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis gang ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1350: shin tu gang ba gnyis kyi mi g.yo ba la
NK015(ba)025:1351: sogs des 'dres shing de dag gi don zhal las
NK015(ba)025:1353: ces sogs yig brgya brjod pas dpang po'i lha rnams rang la bstim mo //
NK015(ba)025:1354: badga gisa dge ba'i lasa ni man+dala phul ba 'di bgyis pasa /
NK015(ba)025:1355: 'jiga rten 'dir dus ringa pora mi thoga sangsa rgyas nasa /
NK015(ba)025:1356: sprul pa de kun gyi 'gro ba rnams la phana phyir dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor nas /
NK015(ba)025:1357: semsa can sdug bsngal mang ste 'khor ba spyi dang
NK015(ba)025:1358: bye brag gi sdug bsngal gyis gdung ba las grol
NK015(ba)025:1359: bar gyur cig / ces smon lam btab pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1360: longs sku'i man+dala ni gsang snying gi le'u dgu pa nas bshad cing /
NK015(ba)025:1361: sprul sku'i man+da la ni sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu pa las bshad do //
NK015(ba)025:1362: man+da la rim gsum rdzogs so //
NK015(ba)025:1364: // spyi don gnyis pa sngon 'gro dngos la /
NK015(ba)025:1369: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa rnams rim par snang yang /
NK015(ba)025:1370: 'dir phyag len la mtshams bcad bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1372: bshags pa bya ba dang gsum las /
NK015(ba)025:1373: dang po mtshams bcad pa la /
NK015(ba)025:1374: sngon du skyabs 'gro bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1375: mtshams bcad dngos dang gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:1377: skyabs yul dkon mchog drug po mdun gyi nam mkhar gsal btab la /
NK015(ba)025:1382: 'dir bdag gzhan nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can
NK015(ba)025:1383: thams cad 'khor ba la nges par 'byung nas thar
NK015(ba)025:1384: pa bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'i don
NK015(ba)025:1385: du skyabs 'gro byed bsam pa dang bcas shing /
NK015(ba)025:1389: dge 'dun la lam bgrod pa'i grogs /
NK015(ba)025:1390: yi dam gyi rgyud smin mkha' 'gro chos skyong gis
NK015(ba)025:1391: dngos grub stsol zhing bar chad bsal ba'i tshul du
NK015(ba)025:1392: skyabs 'gro bya'o // de ltar skyabs 'gro sems bskyed tshad med pa bzhi dang bcas pa tshar nas /
NK015(ba)025:1393: dkar gtor yod na skabs 'dir bsngo'o //
NK015(ba)025:1395: 'phags rgyal mchod cing phyi rol pa //
NK015(ba)025:1396: bcu bzhi mnyes dang gnyis po yang //
NK015(ba)025:1397: sbyin pas tshim byas bsgo bar bya //
NK015(ba)025:1400: nyan pa la ni mi dbang ba //
NK015(ba)025:1401: kun kyang re ba bskang lags kyis //
NK015(ba)025:1403: stod zur ba tshang gis lugs la /
NK015(ba)025:1405: cha gsum dpal sdom ma zhes bya ba gcig gis bsngo bar bshad /
NK015(ba)025:1406: 'dir dam pa yab sras kyi lugs la dbang dang bsgrub pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:1407: srungs ma bco lnga la rgyas par bsngo la /
NK015(ba)025:1408: 'dir re zhig sngags drug phyag drug gis bsngo ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:1409: bskang ba tshogs mchod kyis dus kyis dbang btsan no //
NK015(ba)025:1411: lta ba don gyis mtshams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1412: mtshan ma rtags kyi mtshams gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:1415: ye shes 'khor lo skad cig mas //
NK015(ba)025:1416: rnam rtog log 'dren bgegs rnams bskrad //
NK015(ba)025:1417: ces pa ltar go bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:1418: gnyis pa mtshan ma rtags kyi mtshams la /
NK015(ba)025:1423: slob dpon pad+ma dang rgyal ba yang dgon pa gnyis kyis gsungs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1424: rgyas pa dang thabs zhags ltar /
NK015(ba)025:1425: zhi ba mtshon cha'i mtshams rnams yod pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1426: gong ma gnyis ni logs su shes la /
NK015(ba)025:1429: spyir rtsod ldan snyigs ma'i dus 'dir /
NK015(ba)025:1430: mi rnams dge ba'i las mi spyod cing 'dod pa nyung bas /
NK015(ba)025:1431: dkar phyogs chos skyong ba'i srungs ma rnams mthu chung zhing nus pa nyams pa yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:1432: mi dge ba'i las la brtson zhing log lta shas che bas /
NK015(ba)025:1433: nag po'i phyogs kyi bdud rigs rnams kha rgyal zhing nus pa che bas /
NK015(ba)025:1434: chos snying nas bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la bar chad shin tu rgod pa yin /
NK015(ba)025:1435: khyad par du rgyal po be kar gyis skye bo phal pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:1436: chos la zhugs pa rnams kyi shes rgyud byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK015(ba)025:1437: shes pa ring du mi gnas shing /
NK015(ba)025:1438: log pa'i lam la sbyor bar bshad yod pas /
NK015(ba)025:1439: bsgrub pa po rnams la bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom pa 'di kho na gal che bar gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:1440: de la 'khor gyi rim pa drug yod pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1441: thog mar byang chub sems kyi bsrung ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:1442: bdag la sdang bar byed pa'i dgra /
NK015(ba)025:1444: thar ba dang thams cad mkhyen pa bsgrub pa la bar du gcod par byed pa'i /
NK015(ba)025:1445: gnod byed gdug pa can rnams kyi gtsor byas pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1446: ma nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK015(ba)025:1447: bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur
NK015(ba)025:1448: cig / sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)025:1449: myur du byang chub rin po che thob par bya ba'i ched du /
NK015(ba)025:1450: rang lam rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK015(ba)025:1451: de'i ched du spyir sangs ma rgyas kyi bar du lus ngag yid gsum dge ba la bkol /
NK015(ba)025:1452: dgos nam ma shi'i bar du lus ngag yid gsum dge ba la bkol /
NK015(ba)025:1453: yang dgos dus da lta nas bzung ste sang nyi
NK015(ba)025:1454: ma de tsam bar du lus ngag yid gsum dge
NK015(ba)025:1455: bar bkol snyam du dar gcig bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:1456: de bsrung ba thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur pa yin /
NK015(ba)025:1457: gnod byed kho rang gi don du byang chub bsgrub pa la /
NK015(ba)025:1458: kho rang gi bar chad byed mi srid pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:1459: skyel ma dgra la bcol bas /
NK015(ba)025:1460: 'jigs med lam du skyel ba dang 'dra'o //
NK015(ba)025:1461: de ltar mi dang mi ma yin pa'i 'jigs pa
NK015(ba)025:1462: brgyad dang bcu drug la sogs pa ma lus bsrung
NK015(ba)025:1463: bar byed pa byang chub sems kyi bsrung ba 'di
NK015(ba)025:1464: yin no // de nas yul ris rgyal khams bsrung ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:1465: gtum po gsum brtsegs gi bsrung ba 'di bsgom ste /
NK015(ba)025:1466: gar sdod pa'i sa phyogs de dag thams cad /
NK015(ba)025:1467: rje btsun thugs rje chen po yi ge drug pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1468: sku shin tu che ba gcig bsgom mthong ba tsam
NK015(ba)025:1469: gyis 'gro ba thams cad kyi bsam ngan sbyor rtsub
NK015(ba)025:1470: thams cad zhi zhing rgyud byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK015(ba)025:1471: dang ldan par byed pa'i phrin las can de lta
NK015(ba)025:1472: bu gcig bsgom / de'i thugs kar rje btsun khro
NK015(ba)025:1473: bo'i rgyal po 'phags pa mi g.yo ba dus gsum
NK015(ba)025:1474: gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phrin las kyi ngo
NK015(ba)025:1475: bu gcig bsgom / bor gyur pa / mthong thos
NK015(ba)025:1476: dran pa tsam gyis phyi nang gi bgegs thams cad
NK015(ba)025:1477: zhi zhing bar chad thams cad bsrung bar byed pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1479: de'i thugs kar rang yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa de gsal bar bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:1480: de nas yul phyogs dang nye 'khor bsrung ba la
NK015(ba)025:1481: sogs pa'i go cha lnga'i bsrung ba 'di bsgom ste
NK015(ba)025:1482: / rang nyid skad cig gis yi dam lhar gsal
NK015(ba)025:1483: ba'i thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK015(ba)025:1484: rang dang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs
NK015(ba)025:1485: / te / spyi bor 'od du zhu ba las
NK015(ba)025:1486: thim pa nas srog dag pa'i rtsa'i nang rdo rje
NK015(ba)025:1487: lu gu rgyud du gyur nas /
NK015(ba)025:1488: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram gyis rgyas gdab par bsgom ste /
NK015(ba)025:1490: yang thugs ka'i sa bon las /
NK015(ba)025:1491: yi dam gang yin pa de'i phyag mtshan gang yin pa las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:1492: bar du gcod pa thams cad ring du bskrad /
NK015(ba)025:1493: tshur 'dus pa las steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad
NK015(ba)025:1494: yi dam gyi phyag mtshan rtse mo phyir bstan nas
NK015(ba)025:1495: / yu ba nang du bstan pa'i gur du gyur par bsam ste go cha gnyis pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1496: yang thugs ka'i sa bon las rdo rje'i 'od zer gong bzhin 'phros tshur 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1497: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad rdo rje'i gur du gyur par bsam ste go cha gsum pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1498: yang thugs ka'i sa bon las mad'i 'od zer 'phros te /
NK015(ba)025:1500: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad mda' mdil phyir bstan pa'i gur du gyur par bsam ste /
NK015(ba)025:1502: yang thugs ka'i sa bon las me'i 'od zer 'phros te /
NK015(ba)025:1503: bar du gcod pa thams cad ring du bskrad tshur 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1504: steng 'og phyogs mtshams me ri 'bar ba'i gur du gyur par bsam ste /
NK015(ba)025:1505: de ltar go cha lnga'i bsrung ba de la /
NK015(ba)025:1506: phyi bdud nag po'i phyogs rnams ni /
NK015(ba)025:1507: gang la nye bar mi nus pa /
NK015(ba)025:1508: nang bdud dkar po'i phyogs rnams kyi nyams tshad cing tshugs na bar chad brtsam pa rnams /
NK015(ba)025:1509: go cha gsum gyi mi thub cing /
NK015(ba)025:1510: de yang me lha mes mi thub /
NK015(ba)025:1511: dbang ldan gyis mda' mi thub /
NK015(ba)025:1512: brgya byin gyi rdo rje'i mi thub la /
NK015(ba)025:1513: yi dam gyi phyag mtshan la thams cad 'da' bar
NK015(ba)025:1514: mi nus zhing srog rtsa rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud
NK015(ba)025:1515: du gyur pas / bar du gcod pa'i skabs med par gyur /
NK015(ba)025:1516: de nas bsrung ba'i man ngag yi ge gsum gyi bsrung ba 'di bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:1517: rang gis lus sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i bdag nyid dkar po gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1518: de je cher gyur pa'i nang du /
NK015(ba)025:1519: rang gis ngag sangs rgyas thams cad kyis gsung gis bdag nyid +aahdamara po gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1520: de je cher gyur pa'i nang du /
NK015(ba)025:1521: rang gis sems sangs rgyas thams cad kyis thugs kyi
NK015(ba)025:1522: bdag nyid yi ge h'u mthing kha gcig tu gyur
NK015(ba)025:1523: par bsam la / de nas lus ngag yid gsum
NK015(ba)025:1524: sku gsung thugs kyis yi ge gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK015(ba)025:1526: bar du gcod pa gang gis gnod mi nus ste /
NK015(ba)025:1527: bsrung 'khor bka' rgya ma shin tu zab bo //
NK015(ba)025:1528: de nas rang byung lhun grub kyi bsrung 'khor lus bsrung 'khor du dran pas gsal gdab ste /
NK015(ba)025:1529: rkang mthil rdo rje'i sa gzhi /
NK015(ba)025:1530: rtse mo rdo rje'i rwa ba /
NK015(ba)025:1532: skra dang ba spu mad'i rwa ba /
NK015(ba)025:1533: so dang sen mo me ri dang me dpung rab du 'bar ste /
NK015(ba)025:1534: de rnams de ltar yin no snyam du shes shing dran par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:1536: ngag tu brjod pa ma yin no /
NK015(ba)025:1538: / 'di dran pa tsam gyis bar chad thams cad rang
NK015(ba)025:1539: 'gag la 'gro bas bsrung ba'i mchog tu gyur pa'o
NK015(ba)025:1540: // de nas don dam byang chub kyis sems /
NK015(ba)025:1541: rnam par mi rtog pa'i bsrung ba bsgom ste /
NK015(ba)025:1542: bar du gcod pa'i yul gcod mkhan gyi bgegs /
NK015(ba)025:1543: bar chad rang gi ngo bo gsum rang sems phyag rgya chen por shes shing /
NK015(ba)025:1544: de nyid kyi ngang la rnam rtog spro bsdu med
NK015(ba)025:1545: par gsal stong nam mkha'i dkyil ltar yid byed blo
NK015(ba)025:1549: de ni bsrung ba rnams kyis nang nas mchog ste /
NK015(ba)025:1550: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgrar lang yang g.yo ba'am bskyod par mi nus pa yin no //
NK015(ba)025:1551: rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud bsgrub thabs rnams su bsrung ba'i 'khor lo mang du gsung kyang /
NK015(ba)025:1552: drug po 'di las zab pa med pa yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:1553: bsgrub pa la 'jug pa'i nub mo dang /
NK015(ba)025:1554: skabs rnams su thams cad rgyas shing tshang par bsgom la /
NK015(ba)025:1555: dus thams cad du yang srod kyi thun mgor byang chub sems kyi bsrung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1556: mtshan ma'i bsrung ba gsum po gang rung gcig dang /
NK015(ba)025:1557: lus bsrung 'khor du dran pas gsal gdab pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1558: rnam par mi rtog pa'i bsrung ba rnams dus rgyun du bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:1559: shing dang brgyag sgrub pa la sogs lam gyis 'gro 'dug byed pa'i dus su yang /
NK015(ba)025:1560: rje btsun thugs rje chen po shin tu che zhing che ba gcig gi nang nas 'gro zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1561: bya ba thams cad ci bder byed par bsgom pas
NK015(ba)025:1562: bar chad gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa yin no
