NK015(ba)025:1564: bzhi pa thabs zhag ltar la lnga ste /
NK015(ba)025:1565: skyabs 'gro byed cing mtshams lha bsgom pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1570: dang po skyabs 'gro sems bskyed ni sngon song nas /
NK015(ba)025:1572: sems can thams cad kyi bar chad bsal nas /
NK015(ba)025:1573: sangs rgyas thob pa'i ched du /
NK015(ba)025:1574: bdag gi srung 'khor phub cing mtshams bcad par bya'o snyam du bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1575: skad ciga stong pa'i nganga lasa sam /
NK015(ba)025:1576: dpa' bo go rje ba'i tshul du ranga nyid rdo
NK015(ba)025:1577: rje semsa dapa'a thugs chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i rtags
NK015(ba)025:1579: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su gayasa gser
NK015(ba)025:1580: gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar bsnams pa
NK015(ba)025:1581: / stong nyid thugs su chud pa'i rtags su g.yona dngul dkar gyis dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK015(ba)025:1582: bgegs rnams tshar gcod pa'i phyir zhi ma khro'i rnam pa /
NK015(ba)025:1583: zhal 'dzum yang mche ba yud tsam mngona pa /
NK015(ba)025:1584: spyan gsum zhi ba yin kyang yid tsam sdang miga tu gzigas pa /
NK015(ba)025:1585: mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su zhabs skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1586: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i rtags su zla ba la rgyab yol byas pa /
NK015(ba)025:1587: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su sku la
NK015(ba)025:1588: 'od phung kha dog lnga ldan gi nang na bzhugs
NK015(ba)025:1589: kyang kyi rtse mo la me ri 'phro ba thams
NK015(ba)025:1590: cad mnyam pa nyid dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)025:1591: snyan gong g.yas g.yon na ut+pala 'dab ma stong ldan re res brgyan cing /
NK015(ba)025:1592: rgyan chas bcu gsum dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)025:1593: nyi ma'i gadna la yum dbyingsa phyug ma dang snyomsa
NK015(ba)025:1594: para 'juga pa yum gyis g.yas yab la 'khyud cing
NK015(ba)025:1595: g.yona dngul dkar gyi dril bu yab kyi snyan rtsar
NK015(ba)025:1596: dkrol ba sku mdog yab dang 'dra zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1598: yab de'i thugsa kara zla ba'i gadna la ranga 'dra
NK015(ba)025:1599: ba'i ye shes semsa dapa'a phyag mtshan 'dzin 'dzin 'dra
NK015(ba)025:1601: de'i thugsa kara nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje dkar
NK015(ba)025:1602: zer yang sngon po rtse lnga yi lte bar h'u
NK015(ba)025:1603: sngon po la h'u badz+ra d+h+rika gis gayasa su 'khora
NK015(ba)025:1604: ba yum gyi thugas kara dril bu yi bum pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1605: nanga du m+aum mthinga naga las /
NK015(ba)025:1608: yab yum gnyis ka'i spyi bo'i 'khora lo la dakara po /
NK015(ba)025:1610: thugs kar nyi ma la h'u sngon po /
NK015(ba)025:1611: dbang dang rab gnas kyi dus su lha dgu nyid bcu bsgom dgos gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:1612: gnyis pa byin bsdu ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:1613: sku gsung thugs la sngags 'di brjod ces gsungs pas /
NK015(ba)025:1614: thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnams su phog /
NK015(ba)025:1615: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas de thams cad chos sku la
NK015(ba)025:1616: gzugs kyi skur rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum kyi
NK015(ba)025:1617: rnam par bzhengs nas mdun gyi nam mkha' bzhugs par
NK015(ba)025:1622: ces brjod dus mdun gyis lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi bo nas dkar po byung /
NK015(ba)025:1623: bdag gi spyi bor thim pas /
NK015(ba)025:1624: sku'i gzi brjid 'bar ba rdo rje lta bu'i mi 'gyur ba'i ngang du sdud par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1628: ces brjod dus mdun gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi mgrin
NK015(ba)025:1629: pa nas 'od zer dmar po bdag gi mgrin par
NK015(ba)025:1630: thim pas / yid skyob cing thams cad kyis yid
NK015(ba)025:1631: la mdzes shing tshim par byed pa'i gsung dbyangs yan
NK015(ba)025:1632: lag drug cu la mnga' brnyes pa'i nus pa dang
NK015(ba)025:1633: ldan pa'i ngang du sdud par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1638: mdun gyis lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka nas 'od
NK015(ba)025:1639: zer mthing nag byung nas bdag gi thugs kar thim
NK015(ba)025:1640: pas / thugs rdo rje lta bu skye 'jig dang
NK015(ba)025:1641: bral ba ye shes lnga'i ngang du sdud par bsam
NK015(ba)025:1642: pas / / gsum pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1646: bdag gi thugs ka nas kyang rdo rje'i char byung /
NK015(ba)025:1647: mdun gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka nas rdo rje'i char byung nas /
NK015(ba)025:1648: de gnyis 'thab pa'i bar bgegs rnams sems brgyal zhing lus dum bur bcad par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1649: de bzhin du b+h+r+aum spyi bo nas 'khor lo'i char /
NK015(ba)025:1650: t+r+aam b+h+r+aum lte ba nas ral gri'i char /
NK015(ba)025:1651: h+r+aib+h+r+aum mgrin pa nas tho ba'i char /
NK015(ba)025:1652: ha b+h+r+aum gsang gnas nas rgya gram gyi char /
NK015(ba)025:1653: sku'i ba spu'i bu ga tshun chad thams cad nas brag ri'i char byung nas /
NK015(ba)025:1654: bgegs thams cad kyi sems brgyal zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1655: lus dum bur bcad par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1657: de nas mtshon cha'i char de dag nam mkhar 'khrigs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1658: bzhi pa rjes su bzung ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:1659: thugs rjes rnam shes slar bslang ba'i sngags 'di brjod do //
NK015(ba)025:1664: sngon byung du rdo rje sems dpas mtshon cha lnga'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK015(ba)025:1665: dz+wa la badz+ra lan gcig brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:1666: phyag na rdo rje yang brgyal nas slar bslang ba yin la /
NK015(ba)025:1667: rjes 'jug gi bgegs rnams kyi sems brgyal ba de slar bslang bar bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1668: phyag na rdo rjes rang gi bka' 'khor la bka'
NK015(ba)025:1669: bsgos pas tshig 'di bgegs rigs rnams la bsgrags te
NK015(ba)025:1670: / rnal 'byor chen po gsang sngags bla na med pa'i dkyil 'khora bsgom pa'i skabs 'dira /
NK015(ba)025:1671: kun kyang gasnga ba bla na med pa'i dam can bka' bsrung so so nasa /
NK015(ba)025:1672: 'du ba la ni ma yin pas ma gtogsa shing /
NK015(ba)025:1673: gsang sngags nyan pa la ni mi dabnga ba'i log
NK015(ba)025:1674: 'dren bgegs tshogs kun kyang rang rang gi re bskang
NK015(ba)025:1675: lagsa kyisa da lta nyid du so sora dengas shig
NK015(ba)025:1676: / h'u ci ste mi 'gro nas bdag gi /
NK015(ba)025:1678: rdo rje 'dzina rgyal rdo rje sems dpa' khros nas ni /
NK015(ba)025:1679: rdo rje la sogs mtshona cha chena po 'abra ba drug po yi /
NK015(ba)025:1680: bgegs khyod rnams thal ba bzhina du brlag para byed pas de bas rang rang gnas su dengs shiga /
NK015(ba)025:1681: ranga gi mig gayasa pa ma lasa nyi ma /
NK015(ba)025:1682: g.yona pa a lasa zla ba /
NK015(ba)025:1683: dbu ma ye shes kyi me dpung du bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1684: h'u h'u h'u mig g.yas pas g.yas skor du bltas pas /
NK015(ba)025:1685: nyi ma las me byung bas gar mthong ba'i bgegs dang log 'dren gyi tshogs thams cad bsreg /
NK015(ba)025:1686: h+aum h+aum h+aum g.yon pas g.yon skor du bltas pas
NK015(ba)025:1687: zla ba la chu byung bas thal ba yang ma
NK015(ba)025:1689: h+aum h+aum h+aum dbus mas thad dkar bltas pas /
NK015(ba)025:1690: de byang chub kyi sems gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:1691: byams snying rje'i sgo nas bgegs rnams rdo rje sems
NK015(ba)025:1692: dpa' chung ngu re re red nas 'jig rten gzhan
NK015(ba)025:1693: gyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams su skye bar bsam
NK015(ba)025:1694: / lnga pa srung 'khor phub pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1695: bsrung bya bsgom pa zhal las shes pa /
NK015(ba)025:1697: h'u nga yi dkyil 'khora bsgom pa 'di nyid brten para bya ba'i phyir /
NK015(ba)025:1698: khro rgyal byin rlabsa lasa byung ba'i /
NK015(ba)025:1699: mtshona cha rnams pa sna tshogsa kyis /
NK015(ba)025:1700: dkyil 'khor 'di nyid kyi rgyab rdo rje rwa ba'i
NK015(ba)025:1701: nang du mtshon cha drug gis rima pa ltar tshul
NK015(ba)025:1703: dang po rdo rje nam mkha' la gnas pa rnams mar la rim pa ltar phab la /
NK015(ba)025:1704: rdo rje'i gur bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1705: h'u steng yanga rdo rje'i bla re la /
NK015(ba)025:1707: rdo rje phra ba dang yang phras gtams zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1709: rdo rje'i thog thog sera chena 'bebsa /
NK015(ba)025:1710: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la 'phur thabs la rdo rje phra ba dang yang phras gtam zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1712: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar rab tu 'khrug pa /
NK015(ba)025:1713: phyogsa mtshams kun kyang rdo rje 'abra basa dza rtsig
NK015(ba)025:1714: gis tshul gyis gtamsa pa la rdo rje phra ba
NK015(ba)025:1716: rlung yanga 'gyu ba'i skabas meda na /
NK015(ba)025:1717: bgegas kyi tshogsa lta ga la srid ste mi srid do //
NK015(ba)025:1719: badz+ra rdo rje dz+wa la 'bar ba la ska nyi ma kro ta khro bo /
NK015(ba)025:1722: khro bo'am rdo rje mthing nag nyi ma ltar 'od 'bar ba'i gur du gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1724: nang ltar na rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK015(ba)025:1725: gsang ba ltar na badz+ra he ru kah de kho na nyid ltar na chos dbyings ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1727: steng yang rdo rje'i bla re la rdo rje'i thog thog ser chen 'bebs /
NK015(ba)025:1728: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhir gyur /
NK015(ba)025:1729: de la rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrug nas
NK015(ba)025:1730: phyogs mtshams kun kyang rdo rje 'bar bas gtams par
NK015(ba)025:1731: gyur / de ltar bzhed pa yang snang /
NK015(ba)025:1732: 'di man chad phyag mtshan gzhan la nges 'dres /
NK015(ba)025:1733: de'i don la sbyar na steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre ni /
NK015(ba)025:1734: kun khyab chen po'i ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1737: rdo rje'i thog thog ser chen 'bebs ni /
NK015(ba)025:1739: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrug pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1740: kun du 'phro ba'i ye shes so //
NK015(ba)025:1741: phyogs mtshams kun kyang rdo rje 'bar bas gtams pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1743: rnam rtog gi rlung yang 'gyu ba med na /
NK015(ba)025:1744: rnam rtog rang bgegs yin pa'i tshogs lta ga la srid ste mi srid do //
NK015(ba)025:1746: phyag mtshan gzhan la yang rang rang gis ye shes gtso bo yin cing des 'dres so //
NK015(ba)025:1747: de nas 'khor lo mar la bab pa gur khang bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1748: h'u steng yang 'khora lo'i ces sogs brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:1749: tsakra 'khor lo dz+wa la la ska kro ta h'u phata /
NK015(ba)025:1751: rdo rje'i gur khang gi rgyab tu 'khor lo dkar
NK015(ba)025:1752: po 'od 'bar ba rtsi bas brgyad pa brtsigs pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1755: nang ltar na rnam par snang mdzad /
NK015(ba)025:1756: gsang ba ltar na b+hud+d+ha he ru kah de kho na nyid ltar na me long ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1757: de nas ral gri mar la bab pa gur bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1758: h'u steng yang rala gri ces sogs brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:1759: pradz+ny+aa shes rab ste ral gri dz+wa la la ska kro ta h'u phata /
NK015(ba)025:1761: 'khor lo'i rgyab tu ral gri ser po 'od 'phro ba brtsigs pa'i gur du gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1763: nang ltar na rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK015(ba)025:1764: gsang ba ltar na rat+na he ru kah de kho na nyid ltar na mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1765: de nas thob mar bab pa gur bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1766: h'u steng yanga thob pa'i ces sogs brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:1767: mu sti tho ba dz+wa la la ska kro ta h'u phata /
NK015(ba)025:1769: ral gri'i rgyab tu tho yu ser po tho mgo dmar po'i gur du gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1771: nang ltar na snang ba mtha' yas /
NK015(ba)025:1772: gsang ba ltar na pad+ma he ru kah de kho
NK015(ba)025:1773: na nyid ltar na so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK015(ba)025:1774: / de nas rgya gram mar bab pa gur khang bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1775: h'u steng yang rgya gram ces sogs brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:1776: karma phrin las rgya gram dz+wa la la ska kro ta h'u phata /
NK015(ba)025:1778: tho ba'i rgyab tu rgya gram ljang ku'i gur du gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1780: nang ltar na don yod grub pa /
NK015(ba)025:1781: gsang ba ltar na karma he ru kah de kho na nyid ltar na bya grub ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:1782: de nas brag ri mar bab pa gur khang bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1783: h'u steng yanga brag ra'i ces sogs brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:1784: badz+ra rdo rje pa ta la brag ri pany+tsa lnga rim h'u phata /
NK015(ba)025:1786: gur lnga rim gyis rgyab tu rdo rje'i brag ri mthing nag gis gur du gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1788: nang ltar na kun tu bzang po gsang ba ltar
NK015(ba)025:1789: na che mchog he ru kah de kho na nyid
NK015(ba)025:1790: ltar na rang byung ye shes so //
NK015(ba)025:1791: de nas dz+wa la badz+wa tshar gcig brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:1792: gur drug ka lte ba nang du tshud pa'i rgya gram chen po /
NK015(ba)025:1797: lte ba mthing nag gcig bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:1799: me ri rdo rje rtse lnga'i rnam pa g.yas 'khor du 'bar bas /
NK015(ba)025:1800: rgya gram rwa bar gyis bgegs de rnams bsregs par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1802: rlung nag 'tshub ma g.yas g.yon du 'khor bas ro bsregs pa'i thal ba yang gtor ba bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1803: zhi ba'i gtor bsngo'i skabs su 'chad des chog la /
NK015(ba)025:1805: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK015(ba)025:1806: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bdag /
NK015(ba)025:1807: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)025:1808: de bzhin nyid kyis dbyings las ni //
NK015(ba)025:1809: khro mo dbang phyug mngon byung ste //
NK015(ba)025:1810: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK015(ba)025:1811: ha la ha la ha la h'u ces brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:1812: rdo rje sems dpa' 'di nyid ngo bo mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)025:1813: yang rnam pa 'gyur bas dpa' bo go rje ba'i
NK015(ba)025:1814: tshul du / bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po dbu dgu brgya phrag stong brgyad brgya /
NK015(ba)025:1816: phyag na stong khams kyi mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa /
NK015(ba)025:1817: thugs ka nas khro mo dbang phyug ma phyung nas
NK015(ba)025:1818: sbyor ba mdzad pa'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems
NK015(ba)025:1819: sprin las / khro bo sku tshad stong gsum tsam
NK015(ba)025:1820: las grangs stong khams kyi rdul phra mo snyed spros
NK015(ba)025:1821: sprin las / pas / bgegs rnams mi gnas par byas nas /
NK015(ba)025:1822: tshur 'dus pas gur drug gi nang khro bo 'chol ba'i gur du gyur par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1823: phur pa ltar na rang gzhung bzhin no //
NK015(ba)025:1824: yang na mtshams bcad kyi skabs su dam pas 'di ltar du gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:1825: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal /
NK015(ba)025:1827: lta ba chos nyid kyi bsrung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:1830: dang po lta ba gdengs dang ldan pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1831: gnyis pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin mtshon cha'i gur dang ldan pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:1832: gsum pa ni bsrung ba'i 'khor lo dape'u chung ltar bris la /
NK015(ba)025:1833: man+dala phyi dor byas pa'i steng du /
NK015(ba)025:1834: me tog tshom bu lnga'am dgu bkram pa ni rigs lnga yab yum du mos /
NK015(ba)025:1835: de'i steng du tsakra me ri yar bstan de steng na rdo rjes mnan /
NK015(ba)025:1837: rang nyid zhi ba'am khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gzhung ltar byas kyang rung /
NK015(ba)025:1838: yi dam rang gzhung gi bstod pa'i bar byas la /
NK015(ba)025:1839: 'khor lo byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1840: rang gi thugs ka nas mdun du b+h+r+aum spros pas 'od du zhu /
NK015(ba)025:1841: mtshon cha lnga'i gur gzhung ltar bskyed 'khor lo dang
NK015(ba)025:1842: gur de'i nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du
NK015(ba)025:1845: sgyu 'phrul lam thabs zhags ltar sku mdog phyag mtshan
NK015(ba)025:1846: rgyan cha lugs gsal bar bsgom thugs kar rang rang
NK015(ba)025:1847: gi phyag mtshan la rang rang gi sa bon gnas
NK015(ba)025:1850: tshe'i ngo bo a dkar por byas te /
NK015(ba)025:1851: so so'i sa bon la bstim /
NK015(ba)025:1855: bsnyen pa brgya rtsa yan chad ci rigs pa bya /
NK015(ba)025:1856: 'dod gsol gdab de nas 'khor lo blang ba'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:1857: 'khor lo la 'khor lo chad de bsgrub bya'i grangs su 'phel bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1858: bsrung ba'i tshigs bcad gang rung brjod /
NK015(ba)025:1859: de nas legs par dril la /
NK015(ba)025:1860: mgul lam lus la btag go //
NK015(ba)025:1862: h'u cis kyang mi tshugs mi shig pa'i //
NK015(ba)025:1863: stong pa'i go cha bla na med //
NK015(ba)025:1864: mtshan ma'i yul rnams bcom nas ni //
NK015(ba)025:1865: chos nyid 'ba' ba'i go bkon no //
NK015(ba)025:1866: h'u cis kyang mi tshugs mi shig pa'i /
NK015(ba)025:1868: / 'khor lo'i go cha bla na med //
NK015(ba)025:1869: gti mug yul rnams bcom nas ni /
NK015(ba)025:1872: h'u cis kyang mi tshugs mi shig pa'i //
NK015(ba)025:1873: rin chen go cha bla na med //
NK015(ba)025:1874: nga rgyal yul rnams bcom nas ni //
NK015(ba)025:1875: rin chen 'bar ba'i go bkon no //
NK015(ba)025:1876: h'u cis kyang mi tshugs mi shig pa'i //
NK015(ba)025:1877: pad+ma'i go cha bla na med /
NK015(ba)025:1879: / 'dod chags yul rnams bcom nas ni //
NK015(ba)025:1881: h'u cis kyang mi tshugs mi shig pa'i //
NK015(ba)025:1882: rgya gram go cha bla na med //
NK015(ba)025:1883: phrag dog yul rnams bcom nas ni //
NK015(ba)025:1884: rgya gram 'bar ba'i go bkon no //
NK015(ba)025:1886: de 'di yan chad kyi mtshams bcad pa de rdzogs so //
NK015(ba)025:1888: // gnyis pa mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa la /
NK015(ba)025:1890: mchod pa byin rlabs dngos dang gnyis yod pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1891: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham gsum spros
NK015(ba)025:1892: pas mchod pa rnams kyi dngos po ma dag pa
NK015(ba)025:1893: thams cad ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar ste
NK015(ba)025:1894: bsreg / yam las ye shes kyi rlung byung bas bsregs pa'i thal ba gtor /
NK015(ba)025:1895: kham las ye shes kyi chu byung bas gtor ba'i
NK015(ba)025:1896: lhag ma yang ma lus par bkru bar bsam la
NK015(ba)025:1897: / de ltar bsregs gtor bkru gsum tshar nas ram yam kham thugs kar bsdu /
NK015(ba)025:1898: mchod pa'i dngos po rang bsregs pa ni ma yin no //
NK015(ba)025:1899: de nas dang po bsang chu byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1900: bsham pa'i bsang chu de nyid mi dmigas pa'i ngang
NK015(ba)025:1901: lasa thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum spros pa 'od tu zhu
NK015(ba)025:1902: ba las snod b+han d+har bsam /
NK015(ba)025:1903: de'i nanga du +aah'oda du zhu ba lasa zla ba
NK015(ba)025:1904: de'i steng du yig 'bru mum mthing nag bsam pa
NK015(ba)025:1905: 'od du zhu ba lasa yum kro ti shwa ri
NK015(ba)025:1906: ste khro mo dbang phyug ma sku mdoga mthing naga
NK015(ba)025:1907: zhal gciga phyag gnyisa pa zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum /
NK015(ba)025:1908: g.yas khro bo'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'dzin pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1909: khu tshur bzlog pa'i rtse mo tshang phug tu gtad
NK015(ba)025:1910: pa / g.yon khro bo'i dril bu dkur brten pa'i tshur du bsnamsa pa /
NK015(ba)025:1913: stag gi sham thabs ste mnabs pa'i rgyan gsum /
NK015(ba)025:1914: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi phreng ba se ral khar thogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1915: skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan pa /
NK015(ba)025:1916: ra ri'i dpung rgyan ste thod pa tshar gsum gcig /
NK015(ba)025:1917: yan la gi tshig mdo rnams su keng rus las
NK015(ba)025:1918: bzos pa'i phreng ba zhing rgyus kyi lung byas pa
NK015(ba)025:1922: thal chen tshom bu ste byug pa'i rgyan gsum /
NK015(ba)025:1923: de ltar dapala gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa de'i
NK015(ba)025:1924: thugsa kara zla ba'i steng du b+han+d+ha de'i nang du
NK015(ba)025:1926: de'i mtha' skor du badz+ra d+ha du kro ti shwa
NK015(ba)025:1927: ri de wi sho d+ha ni sta na dz+ny+aa na
NK015(ba)025:1928: h'u h'u h'u ces pas 'khor bar bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:1929: ngag tu nyer gcig brjod do //
NK015(ba)025:1931: ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyis mgo 'dren /
NK015(ba)025:1940: h'u h'u h'u gyi sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du sdud cig pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:1941: rdo rje dbyings kyis khro mo dbang phyug mas /
NK015(ba)025:1943: ye nas rnam par dag par spyod pa ye shes lnga'i ngang du sgrol cig /
NK015(ba)025:1944: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs su sdud cig pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:1945: sngags bzla dus dmigs pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1946: dbyings phyug ma'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros 'byung ba bzhi la phog /
NK015(ba)025:1947: 'byung ba bzhi lha mo bzhir gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:1951: rlung dam tshig sgrol mar gyur nas /
NK015(ba)025:1952: dbyings phyug ma'i thugs kar thim par bsgom la /
NK015(ba)025:1953: dmigs pa rgyun mi chad par bya zhing /
NK015(ba)025:1954: mthar dbyings phyug ma 'od du zhu nas chos kyi
NK015(ba)025:1955: dbyings kyi rang bzhin du gyur cing 'dzin pa dang
NK015(ba)025:1957: rdo rjes chu dang po gnas khang la gtor bas
NK015(ba)025:1958: gnas khang de nyid zhi khro gang sgom gyi gzhal
NK015(ba)025:1959: yas khang du gyur te byin gyis rlabs /
NK015(ba)025:1960: chu gnyis pa bdag dang mched grogs la gtor bas bdag zhi khro gang yin gyi gtso bor gsal /
NK015(ba)025:1962: lan gsum pa mchod rdzas rnams la gtor bas mchod rdzas kyi dngos po stong par sbyang ngo //
NK015(ba)025:1963: mchod pa byin rlabs dngos ni /
NK015(ba)025:1965: p+au tsa lnga dang gsum bsham brlab //
NK015(ba)025:1967: rtsa ba nang gi p+au tsa brlab pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:1968: yan lag spyi'i p+au tsa brlab thabs gnyis snang ba las /
NK015(ba)025:1969: 'dir dang po la yan lag gam spyi'i mchod pa rnam lnga byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:1970: bi ma la'i byin rlabs phreng ba ltar na /
NK015(ba)025:1971: mchod rdzas mi dmigs pa las /
NK015(ba)025:1972: rang gi thugs ka nas h'u dkar ser dmar ljang
NK015(ba)025:1973: mthing ka rnams spros pas mchod pa rnams la phog
NK015(ba)025:1975: badz+ra ar+g+ham rdo rje mchod yon +aahh'u ma skyes pa'i
NK015(ba)025:1976: ngang nas s+w+aa h+aa ni gzhi tshug par gyur cig
NK015(ba)025:1977: pa ste / h'u dkar mo las lha mo mchod
NK015(ba)025:1978: yon ma dkar mo phyag na mchod yon thogs pa
NK015(ba)025:1979: dpag tu med par byin gyis rlabs /
NK015(ba)025:1980: badz+ra d+hu pe bdug spos a h+aum s+w+aa h+aa h'u
NK015(ba)025:1981: sngon mo las bdug spos ma sngon mo phyag na
NK015(ba)025:1983: badz+ra push+pe me tog ma h'u ser mo las me
NK015(ba)025:1984: tog ma ser mo phyag na me tog thogs pa
NK015(ba)025:1985: / badz+ra a lo ke mar me h'u dmar po
NK015(ba)025:1986: las mar me ma dkar mo phyag na mar me
NK015(ba)025:1987: / bsnams pa / badz+ra g+han+d+he dri chab /
NK015(ba)025:1988: h'u ljang ku las dri chab ma ljang gu phyag na dri'i dung chos thogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1990: h'u mthing ka las zhal zas ma mthing ka phyag na zhal zas thogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1992: h'u khra mo las rol mo ma khra mo phyag na rol mo thogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:1993: dpag tu med pa byin gyis rlabs so /
NK015(ba)025:1995: / 'bul dus yon chab mas zhal dang /
NK015(ba)025:2000: dri chab sku lus la byug /
NK015(ba)025:2003: yang na mchod sprin rgya mtsho ltar byin rlabs byed lugs 'di ltar snang /
NK015(ba)025:2004: mchod yon gyis snod +aahls zla ba'i nang du /
NK015(ba)025:2005: bcud dkar po gcig tu gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:2006: de las 'od zer 'phros sems can la phog chu 'dzin gyis rtog pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2007: sangs rgyas la phog pas mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2009: chu ru snang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2010: 'og min gyis chu m+aa ma k+ai'i byin rlabs bsdus /
NK015(ba)025:2011: gzhi bo la thim 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2013: phyi ltar chu yan lag brgyad ldan /
NK015(ba)025:2014: nang ltar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2015: bdug spos me tog mar me dri chab bzhi'i snod nyi zla'i ga bur bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2016: bcud bdug spos la du ser po /
NK015(ba)025:2017: me tog la pu sngon po /
NK015(ba)025:2018: mar me ma a dmar po /
NK015(ba)025:2019: dri chab la ga ljang gu bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2020: dang po du la 'od zer 'phros sems can la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2022: sangs rgyas la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2024: sems can gyi drir snang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2025: ye shes kyi bdug spos kyi byin rlabs bsdus /
NK015(ba)025:2026: gzhi bo la thim 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2027: badz+ra d+hu pe brjod pas lha mo d+hu pe ma ser mos spos bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2028: phu la 'od 'phros sems can la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2029: me tog du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2030: sangs rgyas la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2032: 'jig rten gyi chu dang thang la skyes pa'i me tog pad+ma dkar po u dum 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)025:2033: ma 'dzu sha ka la sogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2034: ye shes kyi me tog kyi byin rlabs bsdus /
NK015(ba)025:2035: gzhi bo la thim 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2037: push+pe ma sngon mo me tog thogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:2038: a las 'od zer sems can la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2039: 'od gsal du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2040: sangs rgyas la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2041: 'jig rten gyi nyi ma dang zla ba la sogs par snang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2042: ye shes kyi mar me'i byin rlabs bsdus /
NK015(ba)025:2043: gzhi bo la thim 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2044: badz+ra a lo ke brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:2045: mar me ma dmar mo mar me'i rkong bu bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2046: ga la 'od 'phros sems can gyi don byas /
NK015(ba)025:2048: 'jig rten gyi a ka ru dang du ru ka la sogs par snang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2049: ye shes kyi dri chab kyi yon tan bsdus /
NK015(ba)025:2050: gzhi po la thim 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2052: lha mo g+han+d+he ma ljang ku dri chab thogs par bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:2053: zhal zas ni gtor ma dang /
NK015(ba)025:2054: rol mo ni dngos su 'bul bas byin rlabs mi byed pa yang snang ngo //
NK015(ba)025:2055: rtsa ba'am nang khyad par can gyis dam rdzas byin gyis rlabs pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2059: de yang dang po sman gyi byin rlabs las /
NK015(ba)025:2060: ka p+aa la brtag pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2068: de dag ni rgyas par gzhan du shes so //
NK015(ba)025:2074: sman gyis bsrung ma bsgo ba dang lnga'o //
NK015(ba)025:2076: ranga gi thugsa ka nasa b+h+r+aum sera po gciga spros pas sman snod la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2077: de las b+h+r+aum phra mo grangs med pa phyogs bcu'i
NK015(ba)025:2078: 'jig rten gyis khams su spros gnas khang dang spra
NK015(ba)025:2079: gur dung 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2080: 'og min gyis gnas na yar 'phros pas ye shes
NK015(ba)025:2081: kyi gzhal yas khang la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul
NK015(ba)025:2082: / slar 'dus 'og min gyi gzhal yas khang gi byin rlabs dang /
NK015(ba)025:2083: sems can gyis gnas khang dang sbra gur du snang
NK015(ba)025:2084: ba'i yon tan bsdus te gzhi bo'i b+h+r+aum la thim
NK015(ba)025:2086: b+han d+ha ka pa l+aa yangas shinga rgya che ba /
NK015(ba)025:2087: phyi rina po che sna lnga lasa grub pa /
NK015(ba)025:2088: nang b+han d+ha'i gazhala yas khanga /
NK015(ba)025:2089: mu tig dakara po dri ma meda pa lta bu /
NK015(ba)025:2090: thig bzhi btab pasa ril cha dgu dang ldan para bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2092: de'i dbus su nyi ma'i dkyil 'khora /
NK015(ba)025:2094: lhor rina po che zura brgyad sngon po /
NK015(ba)025:2095: nub tu pad+ma 'dab brgyad dmar po /
NK015(ba)025:2096: byang du e gru gsum ljang ku /
NK015(ba)025:2097: dbus su nyi ma'i steng du byang sems dkar po'i steng la h'u dang m+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2098: shar du dri chen ser po'i steng la dang l+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2099: lhor sha chena sngon po'i steng la s+w+aa dang m+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2100: nub tu pad+ma rak+ta dmar po'i steng la +aam dang p+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2101: byang du dri chu ljang ku la h+aa h+aam gnyis
NK015(ba)025:2102: te yab kyi yig 'bru thams cad 'gag med mtshon
NK015(ba)025:2103: pa'i rtags su log po yin la /
NK015(ba)025:2104: yum gyi yig 'bru thams cad shes rab mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)025:2105: ba mtshon pa'i rtags su drang lo yin zhing thabs
NK015(ba)025:2106: shes gnyis med mtshon pa'i rtags su yab yum gyis
NK015(ba)025:2107: yig 'bru rnams kha sbyor yin la /
NK015(ba)025:2108: kha dog ni bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas de dang mtshungs so //
NK015(ba)025:2109: yi ge de rnams lasa yig 'bru phra mo'i 'oda
NK015(ba)025:2110: zera grangs med pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK015(ba)025:2111: su 'phrosa pas sems can gyi ngag tu 'dzin pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2112: rtog pa sbyangs / 'og min gyi gnas su yar 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:2113: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi gsung la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2115: dus gsum gyi bde gshegs pa'i rnams kyi gsung gi byin rlabs dang /
NK015(ba)025:2116: sems can gyis ngag tu snang ba'i yon tan thams cad bsdus te /
NK015(ba)025:2118: dbus su h'u m+aum 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las rdo rje dril bu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)025:2119: shar gyis l+aam las 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)025:2120: lhor s+w+aa m+aam las rin po che dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)025:2121: nub tu am p+aam las pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)025:2122: byang du ha t+aam las rgya gram dang dril bu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)025:2123: de las phyag mtshan grangs med pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams su 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:2124: sems can gyi yid du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2125: 'og min gyi gnas su yar 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:2126: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2127: slar 'dus dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs ye shes lnga'i byin rlabs dang /
NK015(ba)025:2128: sems can gyi yid du snang ba'i yon tan thams cad bsdus te /
NK015(ba)025:2129: gzhi bo la thim pas 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)025:2130: rigs lnga yab yum gyi sku tshon gang bar gyur /
NK015(ba)025:2131: de la sku phra mo grangs med pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:2132: sems can gyis lus su 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)025:2133: 'og min gyi gnas su yar 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)025:2134: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi sku la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2136: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi sku'i byin rlabs dang /
NK015(ba)025:2137: sems can gyi lus su snang ba'i yon tan ste /
NK015(ba)025:2138: de ltar 'khor 'das thams cada kyis bcud bsdus nas slar thim pas /
NK015(ba)025:2139: rigas lnga yab yum gyi sku yongs rdzogs bcur gyur pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:2140: dbus su rdo rje semsa dapa'a dang /
NK015(ba)025:2141: nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma yab yum sku mdog dakara
NK015(ba)025:2142: po yab kyi phyag g.yas na ye shes lnga dang
NK015(ba)025:2143: ldan pa'i rtags su gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga
NK015(ba)025:2144: pa / g.yon chos nyid thugs su chud pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)025:2145: dngul dkar gyi dril bu bsnol nas 'dzin pa /
NK015(ba)025:2146: yum gyi g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK015(ba)025:2147: g.yon dril bu yab kyi snyan rtsar 'khrol ba /
NK015(ba)025:2148: shar du rnam para snang madzada dang sangs rgyas spyan ma yaba yum sku mdog ser po /
NK015(ba)025:2149: yab kyi g.yas na chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i rtags su 'khor lo //
NK015(ba)025:2151: lhor rina chen 'byung ldan dang m+aa ma k+ai yab yum sku mdog sngon po /
NK015(ba)025:2152: yab kyis g.yas na dgos 'dod lhun gyi grub pa'i rtags su rin po che /
NK015(ba)025:2154: nub tu snang mtha' dang gos dkar mo yab yum sku mdog damra po /
NK015(ba)025:2155: yab kyi g.yas na nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags su pad+ma /
NK015(ba)025:2157: byang du dona yoda grub pa dang dam tshig sgrol ma yab yum sku mdog ljang gu /
NK015(ba)025:2158: yab kyi g.yas na phrin las rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i rtags su rgya gram /
NK015(ba)025:2160: yum gyis g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK015(ba)025:2161: g.yon dril bu yab kyi snyan rtsar 'khrol ba /
NK015(ba)025:2162: yab yum rnams kyi mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)025:2163: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil krung /
NK015(ba)025:2164: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)025:2165: rgyab brten zla ba la byas pa /
NK015(ba)025:2166: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su 'od 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i khor yug tu 'khor ba /
NK015(ba)025:2167: snyan gong g.yas g.yon na shes bya thams cad mkhyen
NK015(ba)025:2168: pa dang ldan pa'i rtags su ut+pala 'dab ma stong
NK015(ba)025:2170: zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan zhing /
NK015(ba)025:2172: rin po che'i rgyan lnga ste /
NK015(ba)025:2173: rgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes par brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)025:2174: sku snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK015(ba)025:2176: dper na chu nang gi zla ba lta bu'am /
NK015(ba)025:2177: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bu bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)025:2178: ranga gi lag pa g.yon pa'i mthe bonga la ma dmar po /
NK015(ba)025:2179: srin lag la a dkar po /
NK015(ba)025:2180: de gnyis kyi dbus su h+r+aihdamara po gcig bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2181: mthe bong gis ma yongs su gyur pa las nyi ma'i gdan /
NK015(ba)025:2182: srin lag gi a yongs su gyur pa las zla ba'i gdan gnyis kyi bar du /
NK015(ba)025:2183: h+r+aihyongasa su gyur pa las rta mgrin yab yum dmar po yab kyi g.yas lcags kyu /
NK015(ba)025:2185: zhabs gnyis 'dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK015(ba)025:2187: smin ma thur du glog 'gyu ba bzhin du 'khyug pa /
NK015(ba)025:2188: dbu skra dmar ser ral pa gyen la bardzesa pa /
NK015(ba)025:2189: ral pa'i gseb nas yar la /
NK015(ba)025:2190: rta mgo ljang ku rngog ma leb rgan /
NK015(ba)025:2193: rta skad phyogs bcur sgrogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:2196: stag gi sham thabs sku la gsol ba /
NK015(ba)025:2197: gzhan yang sbrul dang thod pa'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)025:2198: yum rdo rje phag mo g.yas gri gug /
NK015(ba)025:2199: g.yon thod khrag bsnams nas yab la 'khril ba cana du bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:2201: mdun na mi pham ma dkar mo g.yas lcags kyu /
NK015(ba)025:2202: g.yas su khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa /
NK015(ba)025:2203: rgyab tu ro long ma dmar po lcags grog /
NK015(ba)025:2204: g.yon du ral gcig ma nag mo dril bu can bzhi dang 'khril sbyor du bsgom pa yang snang /
NK015(ba)025:2205: de nas rang yi dam dang rta mgrin rigs lnga
NK015(ba)025:2206: yab yum kun gyis mkha'a gasnga byin gyis rlabsa pa
NK015(ba)025:2207: la / yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje ni /
NK015(ba)025:2208: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od yongs su rdzogs pa'i steng du /
NK015(ba)025:2209: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK015(ba)025:2210: rdo rje'i dbu bum pa'i nang du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor 'od yongs su rdzogs pa'i steng du /
NK015(ba)025:2211: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyis rang bzhin dkar po gcig bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2212: rdo rje'i rwa dbu ma'i nang du chags pa chos nyid du sgrogs pa'i rtags sam /
NK015(ba)025:2213: yum gyi mkha' la bde ba mthar phyin ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)025:2214: phata nag po mgo phyir bstan pa gcig bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:2215: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i dbus e gru gsum chos kyi 'byung gnas /
NK015(ba)025:2216: rtsa kha kha mu kha 'dus pa'i rtse mo la /
NK015(ba)025:2218: yi ge dmar po rgya mtshal cog la ma lta bu gcig bsam sa ma ya ho /
NK015(ba)025:2219: yum gyi yab la sbyor pa mdzod cig par bskul bas /
NK015(ba)025:2221: yab kyis sbyor ba byed pa zhal gyis bzhes /
NK015(ba)025:2222: a nu r+aa ga ya mi yum gyis yab la sbyor ba myur du mdzod cig par bskul bas /
NK015(ba)025:2223: a nu ra ga ya h'u yab kyis yum la
NK015(ba)025:2224: sbyor ba myur du bya ba zhal gyi bzhes nas
NK015(ba)025:2225: / dza lcags kyu mas dpung pa nas 'khyud /
NK015(ba)025:2226: h'u zhags pa mas lus la 'khril /
NK015(ba)025:2227: bam lcags sgrogs mas mkha' dang mkha' zhal dang zhal du sprad par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:2228: ho dril bu mas bde ba dus gcig nyams su myong ste /
NK015(ba)025:2229: bdag yab yum rol pa madzada pa madzada pa'i byang chub kyis semsa yum gyi mkha' la phab pas /
NK015(ba)025:2230: de'i 'od zera gsang ba'i sbyor mtshams nas 'phros rta mgrina yab yum la phoga /
NK015(ba)025:2231: rta mgrin yab yum rola pa mdzad pa'i byang chub
NK015(ba)025:2232: semsa kyis 'oda zer rigas lnga yab yum bcu la
NK015(ba)025:2233: phoga / rigas lnga yab yum bcu rol pa madzada
NK015(ba)025:2234: pa'i byang chub semas kyi 'oda zera phyogsa bcu'i sangsa
NK015(ba)025:2235: rgyas thams cada la phoga pas thugs dam gyi rgyud
NK015(ba)025:2236: phoga / bskul / de daga rol pa madzada pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2237: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer thugsa chosa nyid kyi
NK015(ba)025:2238: bdud rtsi kha dog lnga ldan tshur 'dusa rigas lnga
NK015(ba)025:2239: yaba yum bcu la gcig char du thim para bsam
NK015(ba)025:2240: phoga / bskul / pa'am / yang na sngags bzlas pa dang rim gyis sprad pa /
NK015(ba)025:2241: bdag yab yum rol pa mdzad pa'i 'od zer rta mgrin yab yum la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2242: rta mgrin yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer /
NK015(ba)025:2244: de yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer rnam snang la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2245: de yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer rin 'byung la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2246: de yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer snang mtha' la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2247: de yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer don grub la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2248: de yab yum sbyor ba'i 'od zer dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2250: de dag sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun mar la bab ste /
NK015(ba)025:2251: dper na kha ba bab pa ltar rigs lnga la thim par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2253: h'u ni rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags badz+ra d+h+rika ni rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags /
NK015(ba)025:2254: m+aum rgyu ma no rtsa ba'i sngags /
NK015(ba)025:2255: d+ha t+ai shwa ri gti mug dga' ma ste dbyings phyug ma'i bskyed sngags /
NK015(ba)025:2256: rgyu dzina dzika ni rgyal ba rnam snang 'dzin pa'i lam rgyu /
NK015(ba)025:2257: dee sha ra ti zhe sdang dga' ma ste sangs rgyas spyan ma'i /
NK015(ba)025:2259: rat+na d+h+rika ni rin 'byung rin po che 'dzin pa'i m+aam rgyu /
NK015(ba)025:2260: mo ha ra ti nga rgyal dga' ma ste m+aa ma k+ai'i /
NK015(ba)025:2262: a ro lika chos snang mtha' pad+ma 'dzin ma'i /
NK015(ba)025:2264: r+aa ga ra ti 'dod chags dga' ma ste gos dkar mo'i /
NK015(ba)025:2266: pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika don grub shes rab ral gri 'dzin pa'i /
NK015(ba)025:2268: badz+ra ra ti phrag dog dga' ma ste dam tshig sgrol ma'i /
NK015(ba)025:2272: sarba thams cad pany+tsa lnga a mri ta bdud rtsi /
NK015(ba)025:2273: h'u cha lnga yod pa'i ye shes /
NK015(ba)025:2275: th+aa bdud rtsi bzhu ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:2277: lag pa g.yon pa dpung brkyang la //
NK015(ba)025:2278: mthe bong srin lag dkyil du 'gug /
NK015(ba)025:2279: tshon gang rdo rje chang bcug ste //
NK015(ba)025:2281: bzlas brjod rlung dang 'dra ba las //
NK015(ba)025:2282: glal dang sbrid pas bar mi bcad //
NK015(ba)025:2283: dgugs pa 'di dag dzapa tu bsgrang //
NK015(ba)025:2285: lag pa g.yon pa bdud rtsi'i steng du brkyang /
NK015(ba)025:2286: mthe bong srin lag rtse sprad /
NK015(ba)025:2289: de la phreng ba bkon nas /
NK015(ba)025:2290: rigs lnga yab yum gyi bdud rtsi'i snying po 'bru dgu sgril ma /
NK015(ba)025:2291: bargya'am nyer gcig gam bdun 'don la /
NK015(ba)025:2292: de nas 'od zer 'od du zhu ba'i dus su
NK015(ba)025:2293: rdo rje'i rtse mo sman gyi dbus dang phyogs bzhir
NK015(ba)025:2294: reg la / rigas lnga yab yum rola pa madzada
NK015(ba)025:2295: pas rigs lnga yab yum thamsa cad rta mgrin ma
NK015(ba)025:2296: gtogs pa yum yang 'od du zhu nas bduda rtsi
NK015(ba)025:2297: dakara la dmar ba'i madngas chagas pa mu tig dakara
NK015(ba)025:2298: po dri ma meda pa lta bus b+han d+ha phyur
NK015(ba)025:2300: rdo rjes lan gsum dkrugs shing /
NK015(ba)025:2301: sku gsung thugs kyis rgyud bskul bar bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:2302: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u hri tha /
NK015(ba)025:2305: de nas rdo rjes sman chu khyor bar blug la /
NK015(ba)025:2306: mtheb srin nyi zla'i skyog tu bsam la gtor zhing /
NK015(ba)025:2307: +aahmh'u byin rlabs rtsa ba bka' brgyud bla ma /
NK015(ba)025:2308: dngos grub rtsa ba yi dam lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:2309: phrin las rtsa ba chos skyong srungs ma /
NK015(ba)025:2310: bsnyen sgrub rtsa ba ma dang mkha' 'gro bstan srung
NK015(ba)025:2311: bka' sdod pho nya las mkhan dang bcas pa rnams
NK015(ba)025:2312: kyi zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa
NK015(ba)025:2313: hi / ces brjod la kha zhag gis zhad tsam gcig mchod /
NK015(ba)025:2314: 'og ma dngos su 'bul ba'i skabs su mtheb srin nyi zla'i skyog tu bsam la gtor ba'am /
NK015(ba)025:2315: lha mo nyi zla'i skyog bzung ba rnams kyi bcus nas mchod par bsam gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:2317: rdo rje'i lag pa g.yon pa'i srin lag gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:2318: khyor ba gang gis bdud rtsi phyogs bcur gtor bas /
NK015(ba)025:2319: rnal 'byor ma mched grogs rnams la phog pas sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2320: mchod rdzas la phog pas phud nyams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2321: sme ba dang mi gtsang ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2322: dam nyams kyi lag nas byung ba la sogs pa nyes pa thams cad dag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2323: gnas khang la phog pas de'i nyes skyon dag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2324: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu la phog pas lus srog sgyu ma rdul du brlag par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:2325: ganga zhiga bka' rku ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2328: nyana pa la mi dabnga ba'i snod ma yina pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2329: bgegas rigas stong phrag bargya cu po de dag la
NK015(ba)025:2330: da'i ye shes kyis bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'di phoga
NK015(ba)025:2331: pa tsam gyis lus srog sgyu ma rdul du brlag
NK015(ba)025:2333: gang zhiga dam tshiga dang ldan pa rnams kyi thugsa dam bskang bar mdzoda ciga /
NK015(ba)025:2334: rigas can rnams kyi dam tshig ni /
NK015(ba)025:2335: rigas meda rnams la dabnga mi 'gyur //
NK015(ba)025:2336: rigas can ranga gi dam tshiga lasa //
NK015(ba)025:2337: sangsa rgyas kun kyang 'ad'a ba mina //
NK015(ba)025:2338: ces rang gi sngags gong ma brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:2339: lce la lan gsum blang ngo //
NK015(ba)025:2343: mtheb srin nyi zla'i skyog tu bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:2344: khyor ba nang gi bdud rtsi'i nang du +aahmh'u gsum
NK015(ba)025:2345: yod pa de blang nas bdag gi gnas gsum du
NK015(ba)025:2347: gnas gsum du thig le bya ba ni dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:2348: de nas khyor ba nang gis bdud rtsi lhag ma de rang gi btung la /
NK015(ba)025:2349: spyi bor bla ma bzhugs par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2353: rtsa gnas thams cad dpa' bo dpa' mo'i rang bzhin du bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:2354: de rnams kyi gsol nas mnyes par bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2355: bdud rtsi gsang gnan gyi mchod pa zhes bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:2356: lnga pa srung ma bsgo ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2357: sman snod ka p+aa la bcud dang bdud rtsi'i steng du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:2358: dper na mtsho la 'khyag ram chags pa'i tshul du
NK015(ba)025:2359: yod pa'i steng du rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo
NK015(ba)025:2360: bo rdo rje byed pa rtse lnga pa'i lte ba
NK015(ba)025:2361: la kha dog lnga ldan gcig bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2362: rang gi mtheb srin gyis rta mgrin tshon gang ba de rdo rje'i rtse mo la bzhugs nas /
NK015(ba)025:2363: bdag la dngos grub ster ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2364: bdud rtsi'i bsrung ma byed par bsam mo /
NK015(ba)025:2366: / 'di ni bi ma mi tra'i byin rlabs phreng pa'i nang nas /
NK015(ba)025:2367: slob dpon dam pa bde bar gshegs pas bsdus pa'i lugs so //
NK015(ba)025:2368: rgyas par bdud rtsi phyi nang gsang gsum gyis byin rlabs logs su shes so //
NK015(ba)025:2369: rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2370: ranga gi thugsa ka nasa b+h+r+aum gciga spros pasa rak+ta'i
NK015(ba)025:2371: snod la phoga pa 'od du zhu bas b+han d+ha
NK015(ba)025:2372: rlon pa lcang lo can gyis ka p+aa la yangas
NK015(ba)025:2373: shing rgya che ba gciga bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2374: de'i nang du tha mal pa'i rak+ta phyi nang gsang gsum gyis ganga bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2375: de nas ranga gi thugs ka nasa ram spros meda dpung gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:2376: tha mal pa'i rak+ta rnams bsregsa cinga meda para bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2377: de nasa ranga gi thugsa ka nas bcud kyi dngos
NK015(ba)025:2378: por dmar po gcig spros pa b+han d+ha'i nang du
NK015(ba)025:2379: bab pa las 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'jig
NK015(ba)025:2380: rten gyi khams su spros pas sems can gyi lus
NK015(ba)025:2381: ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib sbyang /
NK015(ba)025:2382: 'og min du 'phros pas sangs rgyas la mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2383: 'og min gyis rak+ta'i byin rlabs dang /
NK015(ba)025:2384: 'jig rten gyi khams na sa'i rak+ta /
NK015(ba)025:2388: srog chags las byung ba'i rak+ta la sogs pa'i bcud thams cad bsdus te ra la thim /
NK015(ba)025:2389: ra 'od du zhu ba las b+han+d+ha'i nang du rak+ta'i
NK015(ba)025:2390: rgya mtshor gyur ste khrag lbu ri rab tsam chags
NK015(ba)025:2391: pa las / lbu ba'i nang nas rak+ta'i lha mo
NK015(ba)025:2392: dmar mo b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba thogs pa dpag tu
NK015(ba)025:2394: shar gyi rba brlab nub tu 'phyo ba /
NK015(ba)025:2395: nub kyi rba brlab shar du 'phyo ba /
NK015(ba)025:2396: lho'i rba brlab byang du 'phyo ba /
NK015(ba)025:2397: byang gi rba brlab lhor 'phyo ba /
NK015(ba)025:2399: khrag spu ri raba tsam chagsa pa lasa /
NK015(ba)025:2401: zhing chung gi kha bad du chags pa /
NK015(ba)025:2402: tshil chen gyis 'brum dang dar chags pa 'oda zera
NK015(ba)025:2403: dapaga tu meda pa 'aphro ba'i rtse mo la mtshon
NK015(ba)025:2405: ni sngags kyi mgo 'dren ma h+aa chen po /
NK015(ba)025:2409: h'u h'u h'u thugs rje'i sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du sdud cig /
NK015(ba)025:2411: srid gsum khrag gi rgya mtsho chen po 'di 'bar
NK015(ba)025:2412: ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyis tshogs kyis gsol bas
NK015(ba)025:2413: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du sdud cig /
NK015(ba)025:2415: ting nge 'dzin ma gsal bar du brjod cing /
NK015(ba)025:2416: mthar de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la gtor bas sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes shing tshim par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2417: chos skyong rnams la gtor bas thugs dam bskang bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2418: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu la phog pas rdul du brlag par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2420: snying khar rak+ta'i thig le zla gam gcig bya /
NK015(ba)025:2421: 'og mchod pa'i dus su rak+ta'i lha mo thod zhal thogs pa rnams kyis mchod par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2422: rak+ta byin brlab 'di yang b+hi ma la'i lugs so //
NK015(ba)025:2423: rgyas pa phyi nang gsang gsum ltar byin gyis brlab pa'i lugs logs su shes so //
NK015(ba)025:2424: gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa la gnyis ste /
NK015(ba)025:2425: dang po gtor ma gtong ma gtong gis skyon yon ni /
NK015(ba)025:2426: slob dpon pad+ma'i la zhal nas /
NK015(ba)025:2427: gtong dang mi gtong yon tan skyon //
NK015(ba)025:2428: lnga tshan gnyis dang bcu tshan gnyis //
NK015(ba)025:2429: dang po yon tan lnga tshan ni //
NK015(ba)025:2431: dngos grub thob dang nyams skong dang //
NK015(ba)025:2432: ma nyams pa dag mi nyams dang //
NK015(ba)025:2433: phyi mar byang chub rgyur 'gyur lnga //
NK015(ba)025:2434: gnyis pa ma gtong ba'i skyon lnga ni //
NK015(ba)025:2436: tshogs mi rdzogs dang dgra bgegs kyis //
NK015(ba)025:2437: bar chad byed dang bsam mi 'grub //
NK015(ba)025:2438: bzlas brjod chud zos 'di phyi mar //
NK015(ba)025:2439: dngos grub gang yang mi 'grub lnga //
NK015(ba)025:2440: gsum pa skyon gyis bcu tshan ni //
NK015(ba)025:2441: lha dang 'brel thag chad pa dang //
NK015(ba)025:2442: mkha' 'gro'i dngos grub mi thob dang //
NK015(ba)025:2443: sde brgyad la ni bka' mi btsan //
NK015(ba)025:2444: bar chad bgegs rnams mi zhi ngang //
NK015(ba)025:2445: mi dang mi min nad kyis tshugs //
NK015(ba)025:2446: rigs drug rgyud sbyang mi nus dang //
NK015(ba)025:2447: gzhan don mthar mi phyin pa dang //
NK015(ba)025:2448: bdag don lhun gyi mi 'grub dang //
NK015(ba)025:2449: ci dang ci byed thams cad kyis //
NK015(ba)025:2450: lam gyi bar chad mi sel dang //
NK015(ba)025:2451: mthar thug byang chub mi thob bcu //
NK015(ba)025:2452: bzhi pa yon tan bcu tshan ni //
NK015(ba)025:2453: grub thag nye dang des byin rlabs //
NK015(ba)025:2454: ma dang mkha' 'gros dngos grub ster //
NK015(ba)025:2455: sde brgyad la ni bka' btsan sogs //
NK015(ba)025:2456: skyon bcu bzlog pa yon tan nyid //
NK015(ba)025:2457: spyir ni gtor ma'i dgos ched ni //
NK015(ba)025:2458: gtor ma las rab kun gyi mchog /
NK015(ba)025:2459: las rnams kun gyis sna la 'gro //
NK015(ba)025:2460: chos rnams kun gyis gzhi yang yin //
NK015(ba)025:2461: bsnyen sgrub kun gyi rten yang yin //
NK015(ba)025:2464: bka' chad gnas su gyur pas na //
NK015(ba)025:2465: dbang med rigs dang 'gron lam mam //
NK015(ba)025:2466: de min gtor mar 'bad par bya //
NK015(ba)025:2468: gtor tshogs rgya mtsho'i rgyud las /
NK015(ba)025:2469: gtor chu blug nas lag reg na //
NK015(ba)025:2470: phyin chad byin brlab spyod du med //
NK015(ba)025:2471: sa der gnas pa'i 'dre gang gi //
NK015(ba)025:2472: des ni gtor ma de thob skad //
NK015(ba)025:2474: des skyon dang yon tan bstan pa song na /
NK015(ba)025:2475: gnyis pa byin rlabs dngos ni /
NK015(ba)025:2476: ranga gi thugsa ka nasa b+h+r+aum kha dog sna tshogs
NK015(ba)025:2477: pa gciga spros pa gtor ma la phog 'oda du
NK015(ba)025:2478: zhu ba lasa b+han d+ha'i gazhala yasa khang phyi rina
NK015(ba)025:2479: po che sna lnga lasa grub pa la phyogs dang
NK015(ba)025:2480: kha dog / 'dres par 'dod par gnyis la /
NK015(ba)025:2481: 'dir phyag len la phyogs mdog nanga mu tiga dakara po dri ma meda pa lta bu /
NK015(ba)025:2482: thiga bzhi btab pasa rila cha daga dang ldan para bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2483: de la mthu chod du 'dod pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2484: thig sgal du 'dod pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:2485: 'dir phyag len la byang sems dkar po'i thig sgal du 'dod /
NK015(ba)025:2486: de'i dbus su byang semsa dkar po kha ba spungs
NK015(ba)025:2487: pa lta bu'i thog la h'u dkar po rdul chus
NK015(ba)025:2489: de'i rtsar mi ro la m+aum /
NK015(ba)025:2490: shar du dri chen ser po ba bla spungs pa
NK015(ba)025:2491: lta bu'i thog la ser po gser chus bris pa
NK015(ba)025:2492: lta bu / lhor sha chen sngon po'i thog la
NK015(ba)025:2493: s+w+aa sngon po la beed+aur+ya zhun mas bris pa lta
NK015(ba)025:2494: lta bu / bu / nub tu pad+ma rak+ta dmar
NK015(ba)025:2495: po'i thog la +amo dmar po byu ru zhun mas
NK015(ba)025:2497: byang du dri chu ljang ku'i thog la h+aam ljang
NK015(ba)025:2498: ku in+d+ra n+ai la'i zhun mas bris pa lta bu
NK015(ba)025:2499: gcig bsgom / shar lhor glang po che'i ro la lam /
NK015(ba)025:2500: lho nub tu rta ro la mam /
NK015(ba)025:2501: nub byang du rma bya'i ro la p+y+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2502: byang shar du khyi ro la t+aam /
NK015(ba)025:2503: ro de rnams glang sgum du gnas pa'i sog bar du /
NK015(ba)025:2505: lce thog tu bsgom pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2506: spyi bor bsgom pa'i lugs mi 'dra ba'i 'dod pa snang yang /
NK015(ba)025:2509: sems can bzhi po'i spyi bor yi ge rnams bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)025:2510: sems can gyis kha dog yang glang chen thal dkar yin /
NK015(ba)025:2511: rta zag zhur zer yang shes byed ma mthong /
NK015(ba)025:2512: pad+ma'i dam tshig nyer brgyad kyis 'grel bar /
NK015(ba)025:2516: khyi dkar sna mar dgos zer ba snang /
NK015(ba)025:2518: ces rang gi thugs ka nas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK015(ba)025:2519: h'u gis mtshan pa spro ba sha lnga bdud rtsi
NK015(ba)025:2520: lnga la phog / dngos po ma dag pa bsreg nas bcud yig 'bru bcu la thim par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2522: pad+ma a yis mtshan pa spros pas yig 'bru bcu la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2523: de dag thams cad bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2524: a tsan+t+ra man+dala ces zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis mtshan
NK015(ba)025:2525: pa spros pas bdud rtsi'i steng du kha chod kyis
NK015(ba)025:2527: las 'dod pa'i yon tan khams drug gi lha mo
NK015(ba)025:2528: dpag tu med pa 'phro zhing de bzhin gshegs pa
NK015(ba)025:2530: ni sngags kyi mgo 'dren b+ha ling+ta b+ha ling+ta gtor
NK015(ba)025:2531: ma gtor ma te dz+wa gzi brjid b+ha ling+ta gtor
NK015(ba)025:2532: ma b+ha la sha b+ha te chang guh+ya gsang ba
NK015(ba)025:2533: sa ma ya dam tshig s+w+aa h+aa gzhi tshugs par
NK015(ba)025:2537: khyad par du gzi brjid ldan pa gsang ba'i gtor
NK015(ba)025:2538: ma sha chang gis brgyan pa la mi 'da' bas
NK015(ba)025:2539: dam tshig gi gzhi tshugs par gyur cig ces pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2540: don yin pas / brgya rtsa brgyad dam /
NK015(ba)025:2541: nyer gcig gam bdun brjod la /
NK015(ba)025:2542: phyi'i gtor ma steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo /
NK015(ba)025:2543: nang gis gtor ma bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho /
NK015(ba)025:2544: gsang ba'i gtor ma 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus gsum gsal gdab pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:2545: yang na tshar bdun brjod de /
NK015(ba)025:2546: dang po gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mo'i phyag na me long bsnams pa gsal gdab /
NK015(ba)025:2547: gnyis pas sgra'i lha mo sngon mos phyag na pi wam bsnams pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2548: gsum pas dri'i lha mo ser mo phyag na spos phor bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2549: bzhi pas ro'i lha mo dmar mos zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2550: lnga pas reg bya'i lha mo ljang kus na baza'i gong ba rdo rjes mtshan pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2551: drug pas chos kyi lha mo mthing kas e gru gsum bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)025:2552: bdun pas lha mo re'i grangs yang nam mkha'i khams khengs par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2553: kha tshod zla ba'i thog tu rdo rje phyed pas mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)025:2554: rtse mo la rta mgrin tshon gang ba smug po
NK015(ba)025:2555: g.yas mchod dbyug gam mchog dbyug g.yon sdigs 'dzub mdzad
NK015(ba)025:2556: pa gcig gi gtor ma bsrung bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2557: 'og dngos gzhi gtor ma 'bul ba'i dus su lha mo de rnams kyi /
NK015(ba)025:2558: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi spyan dang /
NK015(ba)025:2564: de dag ni nang gi phyi'i mchod pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:2565: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur pa de dag la /
NK015(ba)025:2566: bka' brgyud bla ma rnams kyi ljags 'od zer gyi
NK015(ba)025:2567: sbu gu chu la nyi zer phog pa'i tshul du
NK015(ba)025:2568: gsol / yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gur gyur nas gsol /
NK015(ba)025:2569: chos skyong rnams kyi ljags gri gug gi tshul du gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2570: phyi yi nang gi mchod pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:2571: yang de nyid sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs su gyur nas /
NK015(ba)025:2572: khyad par du khro bo dang chos skyong rnams kyi brjid pa'i tshul du gsol bar bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2573: dug gsum gnas su dag pa'i mchod pa zhes kyang bya /
NK015(ba)025:2574: nang gi gsang ba'i mchod pa zhes kyang bya /
NK015(ba)025:2575: khams gsum yongs sgrol gyi mchod pa zhes kyang bya /
NK015(ba)025:2576: dkyil 'khor gong 'og sngags phyi nang ci ltar na yang /
NK015(ba)025:2577: gtor ma gcig la brten pas chog /
NK015(ba)025:2578: byin rlabs kyang lan gcig byas la nam mchod pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:2580: gsal bar byas la mchod do //
NK015(ba)025:2581: rgyun gtor bskyang dus yi ge 'bru gsum tshar bsdu'o //
NK015(ba)025:2582: gtor ma byin brlab 'di yang b+hi ma la'i lugs so //
NK015(ba)025:2583: de nas bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2584: ye shes sku mchog brjod med kyi bshags pa 'dir bya ste /
NK015(ba)025:2585: de yang spyir chos thams cad la bshags pa'i sgo'i yul rnam par bshad pa med na yang /
NK015(ba)025:2587: rgyud thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i sgo nas 'chad /
NK015(ba)025:2588: lung thams cad mdo bcad bdun gyis 'chad /
NK015(ba)025:2589: bstan bcos thams cad rtsis mgo yan lag lnga yis 'chad /
NK015(ba)025:2590: man ngag thams cad dgongs don lnga yis 'chad pa las /
NK015(ba)025:2591: de la ye shesa sku mchoga 'di man ngag yin pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)025:2593: slob dpon lo rgyus kyi don dang /
NK015(ba)025:2594: rtsa ba mtshan gyi don dang /
NK015(ba)025:2595: yo ga phyogs kyi don dang /
NK015(ba)025:2596: gang zag dgos ched kyis don dang /
NK015(ba)025:2597: sa gcod tshig gis don no //
NK015(ba)025:2598: de la slob dpon lo rgyus kyi don ni /
NK015(ba)025:2602: bram ze me'i thod pa can gyis /
NK015(ba)025:2603: kun du rig pa'i le'u brgyad par /
NK015(ba)025:2604: bskang ba las kyi le'u dpal chen po'i spyan sngar bshags pa byas pa yin las /
NK015(ba)025:2606: dge ba'i bshes gnyen chen po dpal dbyangs kyis byas ste /
NK015(ba)025:2607: slob dpon de yang rgya gar gyis mkhan po ni ma yin /
NK015(ba)025:2608: bod kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen lags /
NK015(ba)025:2609: gdung ni gnyan mi ste ngam ru phug pa yin /
NK015(ba)025:2610: yul lha sa ngan 'phags na bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)025:2611: sku che ba'i yon tan ni /
NK015(ba)025:2612: mkhyen pa'i yon tan khyad du 'phags pa yin te /
NK015(ba)025:2613: slob dpon yon tan dar bas /
NK015(ba)025:2615: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po ral pa can gyis zhal snga nas kyang /
NK015(ba)025:2616: chos skyong ba'i phrin las gtsor mdzad pa /
NK015(ba)025:2617: rgya gar gyi mkhan po pan+di ta spyan bkra ba mang du bzhugs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2618: bod kyi mkhas pa khyad par can mang du bzhugs te /
NK015(ba)025:2619: slob dpon dang mkhyen pa bsdur bas /
NK015(ba)025:2620: mkhyen pa'i rnam grangs slob dpon bas mang pa yang ma byung /
NK015(ba)025:2621: slob dpon gyi phyi nang gi chos bam po brgya tsam 'chad cing /
NK015(ba)025:2623: rgya bod kun gyis the tshom dang gal 'gag sel bar mdzad /
NK015(ba)025:2624: de yang dus re zhig na lpas kyi rgyal po lto re /
NK015(ba)025:2626: kho'i bu lpas lo pho lo chung gis /
NK015(ba)025:2627: pha sha blangs pas 'brom grangs med pa bsam yas pas bsad /
NK015(ba)025:2628: chu khrag gis dmar po song ba tsam bsad nas /
NK015(ba)025:2630: ro la la ma ma thar ba gcig bsang skad /
NK015(ba)025:2631: de'i las kyi rnam par smin pa 'jig rten 'di
NK015(ba)025:2632: na smin pas tsha ba'i nad kyis gdung zhing sdug
NK015(ba)025:2633: bsngal ste / gangs gi thog na nyal na yang gangs zhus par gyur pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2634: lo po lo chung gis ma 'bal za ngan lam ma zhes bya ba yod pa de /
NK015(ba)025:2635: slob dpon dpal dbyangs kyii yon bdag mo yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:2636: ma des slob dpon la dam bskang zhus pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2637: slob dpon gyis don ma gnang la /
NK015(ba)025:2639: yon bdag mo bshags pa ma byas na dam tshig nyams /
NK015(ba)025:2641: yas stag ni shin tu dka' 'o gsungs pas /
NK015(ba)025:2648: nag mo brgya la sogs dgos pas dka' gsungs pas /
NK015(ba)025:2650: de tsam gnang na rnyed zhus nas /
NK015(ba)025:2652: bus slob dpon gyis gnang ngam gsungs pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2654: yas stag mi rnyed pa mang po dgos pa snang byas pas /
NK015(ba)025:2655: bus na re rnyed nas 'ong gi gnang bas chog zer nas /
NK015(ba)025:2656: khong slob dpon khyad par can yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:2657: yas stag zhag gsum nas rnyed skad /
NK015(ba)025:2658: de nas slob dpon gyis btags sam rnyed nas /
NK015(ba)025:2659: bskang ba mdzad pas kho rang gi na tsha de
NK015(ba)025:2660: nyid du slob dpon gyi byin rlabs kyi zhi nas
NK015(ba)025:2661: / slob dpon nyid la de'i nyams sgrib byung nas /
NK015(ba)025:2664: spyan rnams su rnag khrag 'dzag pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2665: de'i dus su slob dpon la ltas ngan pa nye tshe byung yang /
NK015(ba)025:2666: snyung nad drag po'i khar ma btang bas /
NK015(ba)025:2667: rgyud sde mang po spyan drangs nas /
NK015(ba)025:2668: de'i zhal nas dam tshig bshags pa brgya rtsa brgyad mdzad pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2669: de'i nang nas mchog tu gyur pa ye shes sku
NK015(ba)025:2670: mchog gi bshags pa 'di kun du rig pa'i le'u
NK015(ba)025:2671: brgyad pa las byung nas bshags so //
NK015(ba)025:2672: de yang dang po shang gi khrag phyag gis 'dzub mos bkag nas /
NK015(ba)025:2673: ye shes sku mchog gi dbu gsungs pas sems kyis rang bzhin nas mar sleb tsam na /
NK015(ba)025:2675: thugs rje'i gdung 'tshob na mar sleb tsam na sku sor chud do //
NK015(ba)025:2677: rjes 'jug slob dpon de gnyis kyi mdzad do //
NK015(ba)025:2679: don gyis ngo bo de la btags pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:2680: ye shes ni rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK015(ba)025:2682: de ni don dam pa brjod du med pa'i brjod med do //
NK015(ba)025:2683: yo ga phyogs kyis don ni /
NK015(ba)025:2685: gang zag dgos ched kyi don ni /
NK015(ba)025:2686: rnal 'byor pas nyams chag bskang ba'i phyir mdzad /
NK015(ba)025:2687: bshags cing byang bar ma byas na /
NK015(ba)025:2688: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par mi 'gyur ste /
NK015(ba)025:2689: de'i dpe ni snam bu snum zhen pa la tshos mi 'gos pa bzhin no //
NK015(ba)025:2690: de la bshags pa byed pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)025:2691: dpang po'i bskyed lugs mang du snang yang /
NK015(ba)025:2692: 'dir chos rje rin po che'i man ngag pam gsum ma ltar na /
NK015(ba)025:2693: snang srid zhing khams rnam par dag pa gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2694: de'i nang du rang nyid yi dam gyis lhar gsal ba'i thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' /
NK015(ba)025:2695: de'i thugs kar sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la thugs srog gi yig 'brus mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)025:2696: de la 'od zer pam gsum mdun gyis nam mkhar 'phros pa las /
NK015(ba)025:2698: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK015(ba)025:2699: badz+ra sa mana dza h'u dza /
NK015(ba)025:2700: ces lan gsum brjod la se gol g.yas su gdab pas zhi ba'i lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:2701: g.yon du gdab pas khro bo'i lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:2702: dbus su gdab pas sangs rgyas byang sems rig 'dzin
NK015(ba)025:2703: brgyud pa mkha' 'gro chos skyong dpa' bo'i lha tshogs
NK015(ba)025:2704: spyan drangs la / steng phyogs kyi pad+ma'i gdan la
NK015(ba)025:2705: chos sku rgyal ba yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i
NK015(ba)025:2707: bar gyis pad+ma'i gdan la longs sku rnam par snang mdzad la /
NK015(ba)025:2708: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpas bskor ba /
NK015(ba)025:2710: sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa la nyan thos rang rgyal tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)025:2711: de'i mdun du g.yas su zhi ba /
NK015(ba)025:2713: phyi nang gi chos skyong gi tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)025:2714: g.yas su de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku'i rten lugs su blug pa /
NK015(ba)025:2716: ris su bris pa la sogs pa nam mkha' khyab par bsgom /
NK015(ba)025:2717: rgyab phyogs su gsung gi rten gser gyi shog gu
NK015(ba)025:2718: la beed+aur+ya zhun mas bris pa'i po ti glegs bam
NK015(ba)025:2719: +aa li k+aa li'i chos sgra ti ri ri sgrogs
NK015(ba)025:2720: par bsam / g.yon phyogs su thugs rten dang /
NK015(ba)025:2724: de rnams kyi steng phyogs kyi nam mkha' la /
NK015(ba)025:2725: rtsa ba'i bla ma la bka' rgyud kyi bla ma'i
NK015(ba)025:2726: tshogs kyis bskor nas nam mkha' la sprin ltar gtib
NK015(ba)025:2727: par bsgom / de rnams la ja 'dren gyis tshul du mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2728: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha a h'u /
NK015(ba)025:2735: sa gcod tshig gis don la lugs rnam pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:2736: dang po dpal dbyangs ltar na bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)025:2740: sdig pa bshags pa dngos so //
NK015(ba)025:2743: kun rdzob bshags pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)025:2745: rgyud ma h+aa'i lta ba gsal ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2746: lung a nu'i lta ba gsal ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2747: man ngag a ti'i lta ba gsal ba ste /
NK015(ba)025:2748: de ltar du sa bcad pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:2749: gnyis pa zur bzang po dpal ba ltar na /
NK015(ba)025:2750: dbu nas zhabs su bsdus pa'i don la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)025:2753: ci ltar bshags pa'i thabs so //
NK015(ba)025:2755: kun gzhi la tshe thog ma med pa nas bag
NK015(ba)025:2756: chags kyi sgrib pa bsogs pa rnams bshags dgos la
NK015(ba)025:2758: lus kyi sgo nas tsog pur 'dug /
NK015(ba)025:2761: thal mo sbyar srin lag rtse sprad /
NK015(ba)025:2762: ba spu g.yo zhing mchi ma 'khrug pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2763: ngag gi sgo nas tshig bcad dbyangs dang bcas pas nyams pa yod na tshig tu bshags /
NK015(ba)025:2764: yid kyi sgo nas sems gdung ba dang bcas pas sngar byas pa'i las la 'gyod pa byed /
NK015(ba)025:2765: phyin chad mi byed bar bsdam pa'i blo dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bshags so //
NK015(ba)025:2766: ci ltar bshags pa'i thabs la /
NK015(ba)025:2767: lta ba'i sgo nas khyung nam mkha' la 'phur ba ltar du bshags pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2768: spyod pa'i sgo nas glang chen chur 'jugs pa ltar du bshags pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2769: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas spang la me 'ched pa ltar du bshags dgos pa la /
NK015(ba)025:2770: brjod med kyis bshags pa 'di la lta spyod sgom gsum gyi bshags pa tshangs pa yin pas /
NK015(ba)025:2772: lus kyi sgo nas bshags pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2773: ngag gi sgo nas bshags pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2774: yid kyi sgo nas bshags pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:2775: dang po la lus kyi sgo nas bshags pa la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)025:2776: dang po thugs rje ye shes kyi sgo nas spyan drangs zhing bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2777: ye shes lnga ldan glu'i log 'dren /
NK015(ba)025:2778: ye shes kyis mchog ni ci ltar mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin la /
NK015(ba)025:2779: sku'i mchoga ni chos sku yin ste /
NK015(ba)025:2780: de gnyis ni ranga bzhina ma bcos pa'i dkyil 'khora ste /
NK015(ba)025:2781: de ni dper na zla ba nya rgyas pa la
NK015(ba)025:2782: grwa zur med pa lta bur gzung 'dzin gyis spros
NK015(ba)025:2783: pa mi mang'a yanga ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK015(ba)025:2784: sam gzugs sku'i rang rtsal 'gag med du thugsa rje
NK015(ba)025:2785: nyi ma shara bzhina du gdul bya yongs la snyoms
NK015(ba)025:2786: par gang la gang 'dul gyi sgo nas don madzada
NK015(ba)025:2787: pa'i phyir / bshags pa'i dpang po rnams 'dira gshegsa la badga la zhal gyis phyogs /
NK015(ba)025:2789: thugs rjes dgongas shing bdag gi sdig sgrib dag nas
NK015(ba)025:2790: don ma rdzogs kyi bar du bzhugs su gsola ces
NK015(ba)025:2791: brtan cing mi 'gyur bar bzhugs par bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2792: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer kha dog lnga
NK015(ba)025:2793: ldan byung pa'i rtse mo gnyis su gyes pas cha
NK015(ba)025:2794: gcig yi dam gyi thugs kar thim /
NK015(ba)025:2795: cha gcig rtsa ba'i bla ma'i thugs kar bstim pa'i rgyud la phar la bshags tshig mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)025:2796: tshur la dngos grub ster bar bsam /
NK015(ba)025:2797: gnyis pa sku gsum la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2798: h'u cha lnga ye shes lnga ldan glu'i mgo 'dren /
NK015(ba)025:2799: smra bsam brjod du med cing shesa raba rnam kun
NK015(ba)025:2800: mchog ldan gyi stong nyid thabs gang gis kyang mi
NK015(ba)025:2801: g.yo zhing chosa thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur par
NK015(ba)025:2802: dbyingsa chos sku / de nyid 'gag med du 'khor
NK015(ba)025:2803: 'das gnyis la bde ba chena por longs spyod kyang
NK015(ba)025:2804: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi dri mas ma gos pas longsa
NK015(ba)025:2805: spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku rigas lnga'i gtso bor snang zhing
NK015(ba)025:2806: dbyingsa chos sku / / gdul bya sna tshogs pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2807: don du thugsa rje che zhing thabas makhasa pa rgya
NK015(ba)025:2808: cher ston pas rola pa sna tshogs pa'i sku zhi
NK015(ba)025:2809: khro rnams su snang nas don sna tshogs mdzad pa
NK015(ba)025:2810: ni sprul pa'i sku ste de gsuma la phyag 'atshala
NK015(ba)025:2811: dbyingsa chos sku / / lo // ces brjod do //
NK015(ba)025:2812: de la'ang rab 'bring tha ma gsum ste /
NK015(ba)025:2814: 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i ngang nas 'tshal bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2815: blo 'bring gi lus rdul snyed du sprul nas 'tshal bas /
NK015(ba)025:2816: lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs nas 'od zer byung
NK015(ba)025:2817: bas rang gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi dri ma
NK015(ba)025:2819: tha mas lus ngag yid gsum gyis dngos su 'tshal zhing mos gus gdung ba bskyed do //
NK015(ba)025:2820: gsum pa phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'phul ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2821: dngos su 'byor pa rdzas bshams pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2822: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas yid kyi mngona par sprul ste /
NK015(ba)025:2823: snang srid thams cad mchod pa'i rdzas su ma gyur
NK015(ba)025:2824: pa med cing ngan pa'i mchid med pas kun tu
NK015(ba)025:2825: bazanga po'i rdzas nyi tshe las khyad par du gyur
NK015(ba)025:2826: pas bla na meda pa'i mchod pa nam mkha'i sprin
NK015(ba)025:2827: bzhin du zad mi shes pa'i tshogs kyis /
NK015(ba)025:2828: nam mkha'i dbyingsa kyis gar khyab pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK015(ba)025:2829: gyis sgo nas mchod sprin rnam dag rgya cher yongas
NK015(ba)025:2830: su bkoda de bkangs te 'bul lo //
NK015(ba)025:2833: gasnga ba'i mchod pa de kho na nyid kyi mchod
NK015(ba)025:2834: pa de rnams kyi gting dpag dka' bas rgya mtsho
NK015(ba)025:2836: de dag gi rgyas bshad ni gong du rgyun bshags kyii skabs su bstan zin to //
NK015(ba)025:2837: gsang ba'i mchod pa dngos ni /
NK015(ba)025:2838: chos kyi dbyings kun tu bazanga po yum gyi b+ha
NK015(ba)025:2839: ga gsang ba pad+ma'i gzhal yas khang gi nang la
NK015(ba)025:2840: / rgyal ba rigs lnga yab yum bcu'i dkyil 'khor
NK015(ba)025:2841: ni lha dang lha mo ma lus pa dang raba
NK015(ba)025:2842: 'byamsa sprul pa dang bcas pa kun ye nas dus
NK015(ba)025:2843: gsum 'adu 'bral med pa'i don chos kyi dbyingsa su
NK015(ba)025:2845: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su meda pa'i byang chub
NK015(ba)025:2846: semsa kyis dkyil 'khor gyis lha tshogs rnams mnyesa par
NK015(ba)025:2849: chos rje rin po che'i bzhed kyis /
NK015(ba)025:2850: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor kun bzang yab yum gyi sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK015(ba)025:2851: byang sems chu rgyun gyi rang gis spyi bo dang /
NK015(ba)025:2854: lte ba rnams su bab pas /
NK015(ba)025:2855: rim pa bzhin du dga' ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2858: lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba rnams nyams su myong ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2860: rmad byung gtor ma zhes kyang zer ro //
NK015(ba)025:2861: de ltar skyes na gsang ba'i mchod pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:2863: thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas sangs rgyas byang sems rnams la phog /
NK015(ba)025:2864: de rnams kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i zag med
NK015(ba)025:2865: kyi bdud rtsi spyan drangs nas spyi gtsug tu bab
NK015(ba)025:2867: yum gyi b+ha gar bde bar gshegs pa rnams bsam nas mchod /
NK015(ba)025:2869: yang na phyi mchod rnam lnga /
NK015(ba)025:2870: nang mchod lha mo bcu drug dang /
NK015(ba)025:2872: gsang mchod dug lnga dug gsum gyis mchod par 'dod pa yang snang /
NK015(ba)025:2874: sems kyi sgo nas bshags pa la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)025:2878: dang po sems bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2879: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba rang gis sems su 'dus la /
NK015(ba)025:2880: semsa kyi rang bzhina ni chosa dbyingsa ste nam mkha'a
NK015(ba)025:2881: chen po ltar thams cad la khyab cing chosa dbyingsa
NK015(ba)025:2883: de nyid sna tshogs su shar yang shar dus gzung
NK015(ba)025:2884: 'dzin gyis dri mas gos ma myong bas rnam par
NK015(ba)025:2885: daga cing ye gdod ma nas 'oda gasla ba'i rang
NK015(ba)025:2886: bzhin yin zhing / de lta bu'i rnal ma la rang gis blo 'byor par 'dod cing /
NK015(ba)025:2887: de ltar snang stong manyama pa nyid smra ba'i tshig
NK015(ba)025:2888: dang bsam pa'i blo lasa 'adsa pa'i chos dbyings mnyam
NK015(ba)025:2889: nyid byang chub sems la dus rtag tu 'dud pa
NK015(ba)025:2891: gnyis pa lta ba gsal ba la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)025:2892: dang po rgyud ma h+aa'i lta ba gsal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2893: ye shes kun bazanga rol pa 'gag med du shar
NK015(ba)025:2894: ba'i rtsal shes bya'i chos thams cad ma 'dres par
NK015(ba)025:2895: gsal / gsal dus rang snang gnyis med du yongs su rdzogs cing /
NK015(ba)025:2896: de'i gang du gzhan med pas chen po de nyid
NK015(ba)025:2897: ye nasa 'khor 'das kun la bdal zhing khyab pa'i
NK015(ba)025:2898: phyir / phyi yum nang yab gasnga ba yab yum
NK015(ba)025:2899: kha sbyor du bkoda pa'i dkyil 'khora 'dira snang ba
NK015(ba)025:2900: rnams ni log na yod pa ma yin te /
NK015(ba)025:2901: snang srida phyi nang gis chos rnams ye nas rnam
NK015(ba)025:2902: par daga pa lha dang lha mo'i tshogsa su snang
NK015(ba)025:2903: ba yin te / 'byung ba lnga yum lnga yin pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2904: 'byung 'gyur phung po lnga yab lnga ste /
NK015(ba)025:2905: de ltar yab yum lhun grub du rdzogsa shinga rnam
NK015(ba)025:2906: par dag pa ni bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK015(ba)025:2907: lta ba'o // gnyis pa lung +aa nu yo ga'i lta ba gsal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2908: de ltar rol pa 'gag med du shar dus thabs
NK015(ba)025:2909: shes gnyis med kyis byang sems de kun gyis thun
NK015(ba)025:2910: mong gi spyod yul du ma gyur pas gasnga chen
NK015(ba)025:2911: thig le sku nyams su gtar bas raba dgyes bde
NK015(ba)025:2912: stong 'dzin pa la mi 'da' bas gzung chen yum
NK015(ba)025:2913: lnga'i badga nyid ma dbyingsa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha'a
NK015(ba)025:2914: dbyingsa b+ha ga klong yangas pad+mo rang 'khrung du 'khyil
NK015(ba)025:2915: ba'i gzhal yas chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa
NK015(ba)025:2916: ni rdzogs pa +aa nu'i lta ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:2917: gsum pa man ngag a ti'i lta ba gsal ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2918: de ltar dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)025:2919: bdal khyab thiga le chena po'i rang bzhin gyis 'oda
NK015(ba)025:2920: gasla zhing / ye nas de ltar gnas pas /
NK015(ba)025:2921: sangs rgyas sgam pos ma mdzad /
NK015(ba)025:2922: sems can sgrib pos ma bcosa gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa med cing /
NK015(ba)025:2923: byang ba stong pa chuba pa snang ba snying po
NK015(ba)025:2924: dbyer med pa ni chos sku gsang ba chen po'i
NK015(ba)025:2925: sku'o // de nyid cir yanga 'gag med du snang
NK015(ba)025:2926: ba la zug rngu mi mnga' bas bde ba chen
NK015(ba)025:2927: sku'o // po / 'gyur ba med pas g.yung drung chos kyi sku dang /
NK015(ba)025:2928: lha zhi khro'i tshogs su snang zhing snang dus chos sku las ma g.yos te /
NK015(ba)025:2929: gnyis med du rdzogs pa chen po'i a ti'i lta ba'o //
NK015(ba)025:2930: gsum pa dgongs su gsol ba la gsum las zhi ba'i lha tshogs la dgongs su gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2931: de ltar chos kyi dbyings kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK015(ba)025:2932: rig pa'i ye shes kun bzang yab yum dus gsum
NK015(ba)025:2933: 'du 'bral med pa gasnga pa chen po'i dkyil 'khora
NK015(ba)025:2934: du / dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis badga nyid chen mo kun bzang yab yum /
NK015(ba)025:2935: rdor sems la sogs rigas lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK015(ba)025:2937: sems ma brgyad ste byang chub sems dpa' lcam dral yab yum bcu drug dang /
NK015(ba)025:2938: sgo srung khro bo bzhi dang khro mo bzhi'i 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)025:2940: zhi ba'i lhag sdud mkha' 'gro ma rnams so //
NK015(ba)025:2941: khro bo lha tshogs la dgongs su gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2942: rdo rje ni ye shes kyis lha mo'i tshogas kyi rje bo /
NK015(ba)025:2943: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogsa kyi badga po
NK015(ba)025:2944: dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka la sogs pa'i rigas
NK015(ba)025:2945: lnga dapala chena khro rgyal yaba yum bcu dang /
NK015(ba)025:2946: mkha' 'gro ko'u r+ai la sogs gansa ma brgyad dang /
NK015(ba)025:2947: sing+ha la sogs yul gyi phra men ma brgyad dang /
NK015(ba)025:2948: rta gdong la sogs phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK015(ba)025:2949: ye shesa sprul pa'i tshogas chen khro bo bcu /
NK015(ba)025:2950: za byed gsod byed mang po dang /
NK015(ba)025:2951: shar nas ma ltar byamsa shinga /
NK015(ba)025:2952: lho nas sring ltar gdung ba la sogas pa'i sgras nub nas gzung ltar brtse ba /
NK015(ba)025:2953: byang nas bran ltar myur ba ste dbang phyug nyer brgyad dang /
NK015(ba)025:2954: mkha' 'gro rig 'dzin lha tshogs la dgongs su gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2955: gzhan yang legas nyes kyis ltang 'dzina cing dam tshiga gi rjes gcod pa /
NK015(ba)025:2957: phyi'i las la grub pa mo lhag ma la dbang ba rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:2958: nang gi mkha'a 'gro tshogs gtor la dbang ba rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:2959: gsang ba'i rnal 'byor ma lta sgom la dbang ba rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:2960: tshogas ni rig 'dzin gyis slob dpon gyis tshogs dang
NK015(ba)025:2961: bcas pa bshags pa'i dapanga por gyur pa rdo rje
NK015(ba)025:2962: ni ye shes kyi lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:2963: dam can ma tshogs mkha' 'gro'i rig 'dzin rnams dgongas su gsola ces brjod pas /
NK015(ba)025:2964: lha tshogs rnams kyi bdag la thugs kyi dgongs /
NK015(ba)025:2967: ngag gi sgo nas bshags pa la drug ste /
NK015(ba)025:2968: rnal 'byor pas dam tshig ci ltar mnos pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:2969: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob cing bstan pa rjes su 'dzin pa'i gsang mtshan ste /
NK015(ba)025:2970: rdo rje ch+gee mo bdag gis 'gro ba'i dona bya
NK015(ba)025:2971: ba'i phyir smon 'jug gis byang chub mchog tu semsa
NK015(ba)025:2972: bskyed de / bla na meda pa'i 'bras bu byang
NK015(ba)025:2973: chub sangs rgyas kyi go 'aphanga thob pa'i thabs la
NK015(ba)025:2975: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'i nang nas so sora thar pa'i 'dula khrimsa /
NK015(ba)025:2976: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:2977: rgyal ba'i sku gsunga thugsa dang bdag gi lus ngag
NK015(ba)025:2978: yid gsum manyama par sbyor bar byed pa ni sdom
NK015(ba)025:2979: pa'i mchoga ste gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i bsrung
NK015(ba)025:2980: bya 'da' bar daka'a ba'i dam tshiga tshe gtan gyi
NK015(ba)025:2981: gnyer bya la theg pa 'og ma dang thun mong
NK015(ba)025:2983: khyad para gsang sngags bla med kyi bsrung bya rtsa ba dang yan lag rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:2984: lhag pa'i dam tshiga la mdo bzhi brjod bya'i don sam /
NK015(ba)025:2985: mnyam pa'i dam tshig rnams lasa /
NK015(ba)025:2986: snga phyis dbang zhu ba'i dus su mnosa shing dam
NK015(ba)025:2987: tshig 'bog pa rnams kyi don nyams su blang gnyer
NK015(ba)025:2988: du ma bgyis nas dam'a 'o ni nyams so 'tshal
NK015(ba)025:2989: ba ste / zhor la nyams shor ba ma gtogs pa /
NK015(ba)025:2990: gtan nas bsrung bya rnams la ring du mi gtong
NK015(ba)025:2991: zhing don dang 'gal ba'i 'ad'a bar mi bgyid cing
NK015(ba)025:2992: bsrung bya'i bsrung mtshams kyis dona mi shes nas /
NK015(ba)025:2993: de la 'agla zhing mi bsrung ba'i sems kyis ldog semsa ma mchisa kyang /
NK015(ba)025:2994: le lo dang snyom las kyis dbang du btang ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:2995: mi bsrung ba bsam pa min kyang /
NK015(ba)025:2996: gdoda bya da rung longa yoda snyam du sems pa le lo yi dbang du song bas /
NK015(ba)025:2997: lta sgom klong du ma gyur pas rtsal shugsa chung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2998: yang na lta sgom klong du ma gyur pas spyod pa'i rtsal shugs chung ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:2999: tshul bzhin du ma bsgrub pa'i skyon ni /
NK015(ba)025:3000: dran pa dang shes bzhin gyi bya ra ba dang
NK015(ba)025:3001: mi ldan pa'i spyod pa bag meda pa'i dbang du
NK015(ba)025:3002: gyur ste / bskyed rdzogs kyi sgom la mi brtson zhing /
NK015(ba)025:3003: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi yal bar 'dor ba la sogas
NK015(ba)025:3004: nyes pa'i tshogs tshor ba dang ma tshor ba dang
NK015(ba)025:3005: ma riga pa'i dabnga gi ni /
NK015(ba)025:3006: ston pa rgyal bas gsung ba'i daka'a dang /
NK015(ba)025:3007: dam tshiga lasa 'agla bar gyur te /
NK015(ba)025:3008: bdag gi chags nyams byas pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)025:3009: gzhan gyi nyams grib rang la gnod pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:3010: rnal 'byor pa gang zhiga dam tshiga nyamsa pa can dang /
NK015(ba)025:3011: skad ciga tsam yanga 'phrad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:3012: gtam smra bar mi bya zhing /
NK015(ba)025:3013: rgyal ba'i bka' lasa byung ba de ltar ma lcog ste /
NK015(ba)025:3015: nyams pa can yin min dbye gasla dka' ba dang /
NK015(ba)025:3016: mngona shes chung bas skyon can rnams ma rtogsa pa ste /
NK015(ba)025:3017: dam tshig nyamsa pa can dang /
NK015(ba)025:3019: nyams pa can gyi bskang ba byed pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:3020: nyamsa pa can dang snod meda pa rnams la chos bshad pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:3021: dam tshig nyamsa pa can lasa mi 'dzema pas nyamsa pa'i skyon la sogas pa dang /
NK015(ba)025:3022: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa can dang 'grogsa shing bsdad na /
NK015(ba)025:3023: dam tshig nyamsa pa cana de dag gis nyamsa sgrib
NK015(ba)025:3024: gyis skyon gyis bdag la gos par gyur to tshala
NK015(ba)025:3025: rnams kyi / nyams sgrig bshags cing thugs rje'i bzung bar zhu ba ni /
NK015(ba)025:3026: nyams sgrib des bdag gis tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyi sgrib par gyur pa rnams /
NK015(ba)025:3027: rang rab tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis sdig
NK015(ba)025:3028: pa gang byas ngag tu mthola zhing bshagsa na dpang
NK015(ba)025:3029: po khyed rnams kyi byamsa pa'i thugsa rjes badga la
NK015(ba)025:3031: bshags bya'i yul dang bshags byed kyi mkhan po gnyis
NK015(ba)025:3032: su med pa'i chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i dbyingsa la
NK015(ba)025:3033: badga bkoda de / dpang po khyed rnams kyi thugs
NK015(ba)025:3034: kyi dgongs pa chos dbyings mi dmigas btang snyomsa chen
NK015(ba)025:3035: po'i nganga du bzhugas nas kyang /
NK015(ba)025:3036: bdag la bshags bya bshags byed gnyis med dona gyis
NK015(ba)025:3037: dam tshig chag nyams thams cad tshangsa par rtsal du
NK015(ba)025:3038: gsola / drug pa kun rdzob kyi 'gal 'khrul don dam du bshags pa ni /
NK015(ba)025:3039: don dama par bshags pa bya ba'i yul dang bshags
NK015(ba)025:3040: pa byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis su med pa'i gzung
NK015(ba)025:3041: 'dzin gyis spros pa las 'das pa la /
NK015(ba)025:3042: nyams chag gi rnam rtog gang yanga rang rgyud du dmigas para mi 'gyur te stong la /
NK015(ba)025:3043: kun rdzob tu dngos po'i chos kun snang rang rgyud
NK015(ba)025:3044: du ma grub pas sgyu ma tsam gyis ngo bo
NK015(ba)025:3045: la snang ba'i dabnga gisa na /
NK015(ba)025:3046: sdig pa ci bgyis thams cad ranga gnod nas rang
NK015(ba)025:3047: snang gnyis med kyi ngang du bzoda para gsola ba
NK015(ba)025:3048: ni / ye shes kyi lha rnams la bshags pa'o //
NK015(ba)025:3049: de ltar ye shes kyi lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang /
NK015(ba)025:3050: de'i 'khor na gnas pa'i ye shes dang 'jig rten
NK015(ba)025:3051: las grub pa rnams la chag nyams gang byas pa
NK015(ba)025:3052: ngag tu mthola lo bashagas so dam can bka'a gnyan
NK015(ba)025:3053: gyi tshogas / sems gnoda ngo 'gyod do dam can
NK015(ba)025:3054: bka' gnyan gyi tshogsa nyams chag sdig sgrib sbyang nga
NK015(ba)025:3055: bos la lo dama can bka' gnyan gyi tshogas nyes
NK015(ba)025:3056: byas kyi nongsa pa bdag la mchis na mi 'achaba
NK015(ba)025:3057: ste mi gsang nas bshags pas bzoda para gsola /
NK015(ba)025:3058: bzod para zhal gyis bzhesa nas bdag la rtsa ba
NK015(ba)025:3059: dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams tshangs par stsal
NK015(ba)025:3060: du gsola / ces brjod pas mdun gyi dpang po'i lha rnams kyi /
NK015(ba)025:3062: sdig pa chag nyams dag pa'i gnang ba byin par bsam la /
NK015(ba)025:3064: h'u h'u 'phags mchog thugs rje can gyis dus la bab //
NK015(ba)025:3065: khyad par ston pa'i dus la bab //
NK015(ba)025:3066: byin chen dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK015(ba)025:3067: dbang chen bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK015(ba)025:3068: ces brjod pas dpang po'i lha gzhan rnams yi dam la bsdu /
NK015(ba)025:3069: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)025:3070: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)025:3071: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)025:3072: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)025:3073: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK015(ba)025:3074: ces brjod pas yi dam lha tshogs spyi bor byon nas mar rang la bstim /
NK015(ba)025:3075: rtsa gnas bzhi'i rtsa rnams gang nas bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad kyis mi tshugs pa'am /
NK015(ba)025:3076: yang na dbang bzhi'i don rtogs pas phyag rgya chen
NK015(ba)025:3077: po'i ngang du 'bad med lhun grub tu gnas par
NK015(ba)025:3078: bya'o // lhag chad kha bskong la yi ge brgya pa brjod do //
NK015(ba)025:3079: de nas dngos gzhi yi dam zhi khro gang yin la 'jug par bya'o /
NK015(ba)025:3082: rgyun bshags gi sa tik+ka tshogs gnyis phun tshogs /
NK015(ba)025:3083: zhi khro bshags chung gi tik+ka sgrib gnyis dag byed /
NK015(ba)025:3084: man+dala rim gsum bya tik+ka bkod pa'i 'od zer /
NK015(ba)025:3085: dz+wa la badz+ra'i tik+ka bsrung ba rdo rje'i phub chen /
NK015(ba)025:3086: bsang chu byin rlabs tik+ka dag byed khrus kyi rdzing bu /
NK015(ba)025:3087: sman byin rlabs tik+ka dug lnga nad sel sman mchog rgyal po /
NK015(ba)025:3088: rak+ta byin rlabs tik+ka 'dod chags dag byed khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK015(ba)025:3089: gtor ma byin rlabs tik+ka gti mug dag byed bdud rtsi'i mtsho chen /
NK015(ba)025:3090: ye shes sku mchog tik+ka chag nyams skong ba'i rgyal po /
NK015(ba)025:3091: de rnams phyogs gcig tu dril bas /
NK015(ba)025:3092: spyir gang la'ang sbyar du btub kyang /
NK015(ba)025:3093: bye brag tu zhi khro gnyis la sogs sgyu 'phrul
NK015(ba)025:3094: gyi dkyil chog tha dag gis sngon 'gro'i 'grel pa
NK015(ba)025:3095: dgos 'dod 'byung bas rin chen mdzes pa'i rgyan du
NK015(ba)025:3096: gyur pa phreng mdzes zhes bya ba 'di kahthoga yang
NK015(ba)025:3097: dgon du gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin pa ye shes
NK015(ba)025:3098: rgyal mtshan gyis sbyar ba re zhig rdzogs so //
NK015(ba)025:3099: phur pa la sogs pa rnams ni rang rang gi gzhung du shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)025:3100: rmad byung legs bshad gsung gi bdud rtsi kun //
NK015(ba)025:3101: bstus pa'i brgyad ldan me tog bkram bcas mtshor //
NK015(ba)025:3102: bung ba ngang ba'i tshogs bcas rtse byas nas //
NK015(ba)025:3103: kha dog tshig la ma zhen don rtogs mdzod /
NK015(ba)025:3105: / 'di brtsam dge dang dge ba gzhan dag rnams //
NK015(ba)025:3106: rnam pa gcig bsdus bsdus pa'i 'gro ba kun //
NK015(ba)025:3107: kun kyang mtshan 'dzina 'dzina pa las grol zhing //
NK015(ba)025:3108: zhing rnams kun khyab khyab pa'i sangs rgyas shog /
